但系统仍强行买入”**这种情况。  \\\\\\\\n  我继续往下查三个策略是不是走了同一套风控入口。\\\\\\\\nuser: Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\\\\\\\\n```j\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nSource: memory/2026-03-25-1559.md#L57-L112\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"source\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"memory\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"citation\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"memory/2026-03-25-1559.md#L57-L112\\\\\\\"\\\\n    },\\\\n    {\\\\n      \\\\\\\"path\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"memory/2026-03-26.md\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"startLine\\\\\\\": 69,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"endLine\\\\\\\": 109,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"score\\\\\\\": 0.3337199999142089,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"snippet\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"- strategy_governance_gate_latest.json\\\\\\\\n- runtime_risk_state_latest.json\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n#### 当前状态说明\\\\\\\\n- overall=RED 是\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"真实业务风险态\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"（未签收交接单/买入冻结），不是整改未完成\\\\\\\\n- 需要确认：RED态是否有超时自动清除机制\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n#### 设计模式借鉴\\\\\\\\n- 强制交接签收闭环：比 P0-3 设计更严格（execution_attempted=0 也必须交接）\\\\\\\\n- 治理评审机制：回撤连续触发不只是冻结，还需人工评审 + 持久化计数\\\\\\\\n- cron统一运行时：从根上解决环境漂移\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n### RED 消红机制（补充）\\\\\\\\n- 控制塔无 TTL 自动清红器：任一检查 RED → overall=RED\\\\\\\\n- orders_pending_without_execution 消红条件：receiver_ack.status ∈ {ACKED, DONE, CONFIRMED} 且 owner/timestamp/action 非空\\\\\\\\n- 唯一\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"自动变化\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"：当日 close_review 日期不再是预期交易日時 → RED → YELLOW(stale)，不是正式消红\\\\\\\\n- 正式消红路径：人工填 ack 字段并置 ACKED/DONE/CONFIRMED\\\\\\\\n- 参考脚本：run_close_review_v2.py (line 354-390), generate_control_tower_daily.py (line 526-617, 566-572, 739-745)\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\n### 运行态闭环任务（2026-03-26 20:\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nSource: memory/2026-03-26.md#L69-L109\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"source\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"memory\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"citation\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"memory/2026-03-26.md#L69-L109\\\\\\\"\\\\n    },\\\\n    {\\\\n      \\\\\\\"path\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"sessions/0dd9c928-4213-4019-ab83-22b337a4ebb5.jsonl\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"startLine\\\\\\\": 599,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"endLine\\\\\\\": 600,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"score\\\\\\\": 0.3280576586723327,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"snippet\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"day_is_between(context): \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ # \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\uc0\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u20462 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u25913 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u65306 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u30452 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u25509 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u36820 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u22238 False\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u65292 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u19981 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u20877 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u26816 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u26597 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u31354 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u20179 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u26399 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ return False \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ def close_account(context): \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ # \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\uc0\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u20462 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u25913 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u65306 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u31227 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u38500 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u31354 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u20179 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u28165 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u20179 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u36923 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u36753 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ # \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\uc0\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u19981 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u20877 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u22240 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u31354 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u20179 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u26399 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u32780 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u28165 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u20179 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u65292 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u21482 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u22788 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u29702 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u20854 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u20182 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u24773 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\u20917 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ pass \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ def print_position_info(context): \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ for position in list(context.portfolio.positions.values()): \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ securities = position.security \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ cost = position.avg_cost \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ price = position.price \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ ret = 100 * (price / cost - 1) \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ value = position.value \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ amo\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nSource: sessions/0dd9c928-4213-4019-ab83-22b337a4ebb5.jsonl#L599-L600\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"source\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"sessions\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"citation\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"sessions/0dd9c928-4213-4019-ab83-22b337a4ebb5.jsonl#L599-L600\\\\\\\"\\\\n    },\\\\n    {\\\\n      \\\\\\\"path\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"sessions/3b39d38b-6200-4753-bb36-e6142ae6bdb0.jsonl\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"startLine\\\\\\\": 80,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"endLine\\\\\\\": 81,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"score\\\\\\\": 0.33189711570739744,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"snippet\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"Assistant: [[reply_to_current]] 这条**严格说不是某一个模拟盘的买入候选**，而是**合并信号池**出来的预览。 当前这版读的是 `merged_signals_20260326.csv`，TOP3 里这三只 **都来自 `smallcap_chip_v4_2`**。 所以这条现在口径不清，容易让人误以为是： - 防御盘 / 均衡盘 / 进取盘 之一的候选 但实际上更准确的写法应该是二选一： - **候选池来源：merged_signals（策略：smallcap_chip_v4_2 / v4_2b）** - 或者直接拆成：**防御盘候选 / 均衡盘候选 / 进取盘候选** 下次请按第二种或至少把“**非单一模拟盘，系合并信号池预览**”写明。\\\\\\\\nUser: Conversation info (untrusted metadata): ```json { \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"message_id\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"om_x100b536961a51cb0c45d44266a93564\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"reply_to_id\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"om_x100b5368a6a104a4c450510d5391ff7\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"sender_id\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"conversation_label\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"oc_8a819be3a90d35b8d0a2d5c1f4642b22\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"sender\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"张玲\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"timestamp\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Fri 2026-03-27 08:44 GMT+8\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"group_subject\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"oc_8\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nSource: sessions/3b39d38b-6200-4753-bb36-e6142ae6bdb0.jsonl#L80-L81\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"source\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"sessions\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"citation\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"sessions/3b39d38b-6200-4753-bb36-e6142ae6bdb0.jsonl#L80-L81\\\\\\\"\\\\n    },\\\\n    {\\\\n      \\\\\\\"path\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"sessions/0dd9c928-4213-4019-ab83-22b337a4ebb5.jsonl\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"startLine\\\\\\\": 604,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"endLine\\\\\\\": 605,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"score\\\\\\\": 0.3278663158416748,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"snippet\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"* 成本` - 或触发涨停开板卖点 #### 3）策略外/人工混入仓 - 这类才适合按主观逻辑清理 --- # 我现在会修正我前面的建议 我前面那份“第一批优先处理 / 第二批再优化”， **更适用于主观综合账户**， **不适用于你现在明确说明的“这是小市值策略仓”**。 所以这部分我修正成： > **先不要因为单票主观不喜欢就卖。应先按策略规则核查它们是否仍是有效持仓。** --- # 我建议你下一步给我什么 现在最关键的不是更多股票截图，而是这两个里的任一个： ## 方案 A：聚宽最近一次回测/运行结果 最好给我： - 最新 `target_list` - 当前持仓 - 最近一次调仓结果 - 最近一年回测曲线/指标 ## 方案 B：你直接告诉我 - 这些票是不是**当前策略实盘账户**里的全部/一部分 - 最近一次调仓日是哪天 - 这套策略最近一次实际选出来的 7 只票是什么 --- # 一句话版 ### 基于这份代码，我的独立判断是： - **这些票不该因为“看着不够好”就立刻主观卖出** - **这套系统本来就会买很多小市值、质量一般的票** - **真正要不要卖，应该按策略卖点核查** - **下一步应该做“策略一致性检查”，不是“主观清仓”** 如果你愿意，我下一步就直接帮你做： ## **这批持仓的“策略一致性检查清单”** 我会按这套代码把判断框架列成： - 哪些满足继续持有 - 哪些可能已触发卖点 - 哪些只是你主观不舒服，但其实不该动\\\\\\\\nUser: Conversation info (untrusted metadata): ```json { \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"mess\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nSource: sessions/0dd9c928-4213-4019-ab83-22b337a4ebb5.jsonl#L604-L605\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"source\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"sessions\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"citation\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"sessions/0dd9c928-4213-4019-ab83-22b337a4ebb5.jsonl#L604-L605\\\\\\\"\\\\n    }\\\\n  ],\\\\n  \\\\\\\"provider\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"ollama\\\\\\\",\\\\n  \\\\\\\"model\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"bge-m3:latest\\\\\\\",\\\\n  \\\\\\\"citations\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"auto\\\\\\\",\\\\n  \\\\\\\"mode\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"hybrid\\\\\\\"\\\\n}\\\"}],\\\"details\\\":{\\\"results\\\":[{\\\"path\\\":\\\"memory/2026-03-26.md\\\",\\\"startLine\\\":42,\\\"endLine\\\":82,\\\"score\\\":0.3760285205012578,\\\"snippet\\\":\\\"- root cause: aggregate/performance panel treated breadth `nav` as a 1.x ratio instead of paper-capital-scaled asset value\\\\n  - updated `scripts/generate_strategy_performance_panel.py`\\\\n  - regenerated `strategy_performance_panel_latest.*` and `control_tower_daily_latest.*`\\\\n  - verified breadth values now display around `1002476.93` (`breadth_aggressive`) and `1007065.89` (`breadth_strict_oos`)\\\\n\\\\n## 量化系统整改（2026-03-26晚）\\\\n\\\\n### 本轮整改：量化链路稳定性+风控闭环\\\\n- P0/P1 全部闭环，任务板全部 done，回归测试 42 passed\\\\n- 9类核心问题及处理：\\\\n\\\\n#### 已闭环问题\\\\n1. **收盘主链调度缺失** → 修复 run_live_execution_v1.py, auto_run_premarket_precheck.py\\\\n2. **orders_total>0 && execution_attempted=0 未强