{"type":"message","id":"b78953b9","parentId":"8e88c5ac","timestamp":"2026-04-01T22:41:57.337Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_HeqRGY4i91gTOnG1SG9kkSrK|fc_0faca0e75e9e48550169cd9f34ef44819aa7705362e92677c4","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Status: blocked\nPriority: P0\nStarted: 2026-04-02 06:36\nUpdated: 2026-04-02 06:36\nWorkspace: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\nOwner: main-session\nUser Trigger: 张玲在飞书群追问“修完了吗？”后继续指令“继续”\nResume Entry: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/weibo_mcp_auth_blocker_20260402.md\n\n## Goal\n- 收口微博抓取链路，恢复“微博财经大V每日简报”的真实数据抓取；若无法恢复，必须明确真实阻断并给出恢复路径\n\n## Acceptance\n- `mcporter call weibo.get_feeds uid=2014433131 limit=3` 返回真实 feed，非空伪结果\n- `python3 /Users/ling/workspace/weibo-monitor/fetch_and_report.py` 生成的日报不再是“抓取 0 条微博”伪成功\n- 若受外部登录态/验证码阻断，必须落地阻断报告并明确需要的恢复动作\n\n## Current\n- 等待刷新微博登录态/提供新的有效 `WEIBO_COOKIE`，随后注入 `mcp-server-weibo` 并复跑验收\n\n## Next\n- 将新 Cookie 注入 `mcp-server-weibo` 运行环境后复跑 `mcporter call weibo.get_feeds uid=2014433131 limit=3`\n- 复跑 `python3 /Users/ling/workspace/weibo-monitor/fetch_and_report.py`，核对是否不再是“抓取 0 条微博”\n- 若恢复成功，补写回归报告并提交相关改动\n\n## Completed\n- [2026-04-02 06:36] 完成微博抓取链路底层实查，确认当前“0 条微博”不是过滤问题，而是微博登录态/验证码阻断\n- [2026-04-02 06:36] 实测 `mcp-server-weibo` 访客 Cookie 请求 `m.weibo.cn` 返回 `ok=-100` 并跳验证码页\n- [2026-04-02 06:36] 实测 `~/.openclaw/skills/weibo-monitor/config/cookie.env` 中现有 `WEIBO_COOKIE` 请求微博接口返回 `302` 跳登录页，确认已失效\n- [2026-04-02 06:36] 已落地阻断报告：`research/reports/weibo_mcp_auth_blocker_20260402.md`\n\n## Evidence\n- `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/weibo_mcp_auth_blocker_20260402.md`\n- 命令：`python3 /Users/ling/workspace/weibo-monitor/fetch_and_report.py` → 输出 `抓取 0 条微博`\n- 命令：`~/.local/share/fnm/node-versions/v22.22.0/installation/bin/mcporter call weibo.get_feeds uid=2014433131 limit=3` → 输出 `{ content: [], structuredContent: { result: [] }, isError: false }`\n- 命令：直接调用 `mcp_server_weibo.weibo.WeiboCrawler` → 返回 `{\"ok\":-100,...captcha...}`\n- 命令：带现有 `WEIBO_COOKIE` 请求微博接口 → `302` 跳 `passport.weibo.com/sso/signin`\n\n## Blockers\n- 现有微博登录态失效，且访客 Cookie 被微博验证码拦截；在无新有效 `WEIBO_COOKIE` 前无法恢复真实抓取\n\n## Rules\n- `Current` must contain exactly one active item.\n- After finishing `Current`, move it to `Completed`, add proof under `Evidence`, then promote the first item in `Next` into `Current`.\n- Prefer rewriting the whole file once instead of chaining multiple partial edits.\n- After each write, read the file back and verify `Current`, `Next`, and `Completed` before reporting the new state.\n- If prompt context reports `Integrity Warnings`, repair the file before claiming the task state changed.\n- Only set `Status: blocked` when the blocker is real and specific.\n- Only set `Status: done` when `Acceptance` is met.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775083317334}}
{"type":"message","id":"83cd0906","parentId":"b78953b9","timestamp":"2026-04-01T22:41:57.341Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_BtRBEQXuePbCuSj5TBsl4H6C|fc_0faca0e75e9e48550169cd9f34ef58819aabcf7d0db2ed67fa","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 微博抓取链路阻断诊断（2026-04-02 06:36）\n\n## 结论\n\n当前“微博财经大V每日简报”**尚未彻底修完**。\n\n已确认此前的两类代码问题已经修复：\n1. 非财经内容被错误过滤\n2. `mcporter` 输出伪 JSON 导致 cron 解析报错\n\n但现在存在一条更底层、会直接阻断抓取的真实问题：\n\n- `mcp-server-weibo` 使用访客 Cookie 访问 `m.weibo.cn` 时，接口返回 `{\"ok\":-100,...}`，并跳转验证码页\n- `~/.openclaw/skills/weibo-monitor/config/cookie.env` 中现有 `WEIBO_COOKIE` 已失效；访问微博接口时返回 `302` 跳转到微博登录页\n\n因此，当前“0 条微博”不是内容过滤导致，而是**微博登录态 / 验证码拦截导致抓取源为空**。\n\n## 本轮实查证据\n\n### 证据 1：workspace 版日报脚本仍会产出 0 条\n命令：\n```bash\npython3 /Users/ling/workspace/weibo-monitor/fetch_and_report.py\n```\n关键输出：\n```text\n⚠️ 获取UID 2014433131 失败: Expecting property name enclosed in double quotes: line 1 column 3 (char 2)\n📊 **微博财经大V每日简报**\n🕐 2026-04-02 06:32  |  共 10 位大V  |  抓取 0 条微博\n```\n\n### 证据 2：`mcporter` 直接调用返回伪 JSON 且结果为空\n命令：\n```bash\n~/.local/share/fnm/node-versions/v22.22.0/installation/bin/mcporter call weibo.get_feeds uid=2014433131 limit=3\n```\n输出：\n```text\n{ content: [], structuredContent: { result: [] }, isError: false }\n```\n\n### 证据 3：底层 `mcp-server-weibo` 访客 Cookie 已被微博验证码拦截\n命令（摘要）：直接调用 `mcp_server_weibo.weibo.WeiboCrawler` 并请求 `m.weibo.cn/api/container/getIndex`。\n关键输出：\n```text\nCOOKIES {'SUB': '***', 'SUBP': '***'}\nSTATUS 200\nTEXT {\"ok\":-100,...\"url\":\"https://m.weibo.cn/captcha/show?...\"}\n```\n说明：访客 Cookie 被微博返回验证码拦截。\n\n### 证据 4：skill 中现有 `WEIBO_COOKIE` 已失效\n命令（摘要）：读取 `~/.openclaw/skills/weibo-monitor/config/cookie.env` 并带该 Cookie 请求同一接口。\n关键输出：\n```text\nSTATUS 302\nLOCATION https://passport.weibo.com/sso/signin?... \n```\n说明：现有登录态已跳回微博登录页，Cookie 失效。\n\n## 根因归并\n\n### 已修完\n- `fetch_weibo_v2.py` 的 `from __future__ import annotations` 位置错误\n- `fetch_weibo.py` 的 `is_stock_related` 误过滤\n- `fetch_and_report.py` 的 `FINANCE_KEYWORDS` / `is_finance_related` 误过滤\n\n### 未修完 / 当前真实阻断\n- `mcp-server-weibo` 访客 Cookie 被微博验证码拦截\n- skill 中现有 `WEIBO_COOKIE` 已失效\n- 在登录态未恢复前，任何日报都会继续出现“抓取 0 条微博”\n\n## 下一步恢复路径\n\n1. 刷新可用的微博登录态（新的 `WEIBO_COOKIE`）\n2. 将该 Cookie 注入 `mcp-server-weibo` 运行环境\n3. 复跑：\n   - `mcporter call weibo.get_feeds uid=2014433131 limit=3`\n   - `python3 /Users/ling/workspace/weibo-monitor/fetch_and_report.py`\n4. 验收标准：至少 1 个 UID 返回真实 feed；日报不再是“抓取 0 条微博”\n\n## 结论状态\n- 状态：**blocked**\n- 阻断类型：外部登录态 / 验证码\n- 是否为代码过滤问题：**否**\n- 是否已完成全部修复：**否**\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775083317337}}
