cwbM8Xv8FCYTpNo6B3paPFSJcXjAqpxAzaP2vh7bARG8oQ3ObVYFFR5jS2rJhnpcAMvGmluxXMFEAWGCdztbdEl425K1vEGbO1OMLiHvJMzp7pNcFt1cekOQjS5lGxbYGEHn8LtJlKnFSJ1b4RMBcFe-wtdTAp2Nu-CmpH-CtMKZrF2sQ==\",\"summary\":[]}"},{"type":"text","text":"我已经定位出来了：这个 skill 不是完全坏掉，但**监控口径有明显缺陷**，所以会漏报“仓库明明有更新”。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0faca0e75e9e48550169cda0595538819a8da92d0549715567\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 是，**这个 skill 有问题，但更准确说是“监控口径有缺陷”**，不是 Git 没数据。\n\n我刚实查了 `daily_stock_analysis`，结论很清楚：\n\n### 为什么它会说“无需更新”\n这个 skill 现在判断逻辑基本是：\n- **只看 `commits_behind`**\n- 只要 `commits_behind == 0`，就直接判成 `up_to_date`\n\n但它**没把 `commits_ahead` 当成“有新增”**来汇报。\n\n### 你这个 `daily_stock_analysis` 的真实状态\n我刚查到的是：\n\n- `HEAD=84d2e18`\n- `upstream/main=916f7dd`\n- `origin/main=c3e9730`\n- `BEHIND_UPSTREAM=0`\n- `AHEAD_UPSTREAM=10`\n- `BEHIND_ORIGIN=0`\n- `AHEAD_ORIGIN=97`\n\n这说明什么？\n- 它不是没变\n- 恰恰相反，它是**本地已经比 upstream 超前 10 个提交、比 origin 超前 97 个提交**\n- 但 skill 把“没落后上游”直接等价成了“已最新”，所以就给你报成：\n  - `✅ GitHub 仓库检查 | 4 个已最新 | 无需更新`\n\n### 所以问题点有两个\n1. **语义错位**\n   - 它监控的是“是否落后上游”\n   - 但你关心的是“仓库今天有没有更新 / 有没有新增提交”\n   - 这两个不是一回事\n\n2. **实现也有盲区**\n   - 脚本里没有先做 `git fetch`\n   - 如果远端引用没刷新，连“上游是否有新提交”都可能看不准\n\n### 结论\n- **是，这个 skill 当前有问题**\n- 具体不是“完全失效”，而是：\n  - **把“没落后”误报成“没更新”**\n  - **没区分 本地新增 / 上游新增 / 分叉超前**\n  - **还缺少 `git fetch` 预刷新**\n\n### 该怎么改\n我建议直接改成三类状态，而不是只报“需不需要更新”：\n\n1. **上游有更新**\n   - `behind > 0`\n\n2. **本地有新增**\n   - `ahead > 0`\n\n3. **已分叉/已定制**\n   - `ahead > 0 && behind == 0`\n   - 像 `daily_stock_analysis` 现在就属于这个\n\n再加一层：\n- 检查前先 `git fetch --all --prune`\n\n如果你要，我可以直接把这个 skill 修掉，改成：\n- 先 `fetch`\n- 区分 `origin` / `upstream`\n- 同时汇报“上游更新”和“本地今天有新增”\n- 避免再把 `daily_stock_analysis` 这种仓库报成“无变化”","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0faca0e75e9e48550169cda05965f4819abb5e8945af8791c2\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":2737,"output":1243,"cacheRead":63104,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67084,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775083597271,"responseId":"resp_0faca0e75e9e48550169cda04e2200819a9748e1afc41da68d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7f79ccee","parentId":"c9fa6f52","timestamp":"2026-04-01T22:47:04.388Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b53edb8fa90a0c2285935537738b\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"om_x100b53e4d95354a4c4d5ff093c2a107\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_8a819be3a90d35b8d0a2d5c1f4642b22\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-04-02 06:42 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_8a819be3a90d35b8d0a2d5c1f4642b22\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"body\": \"<p>有没有开始修复？@_user_1 @_user_2</p>\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b53edb8fa90a0c2285935537738b]\n张玲: [Replying to: \"<p>有没有开始修复？@_user_1 @_user_2</p>\"]\n\n你直接修复<at user_id=\"ou_c209a91ac6a25a1ba09bc1eb91985a53\">coding agent</at>\n\n[System: The content may include mention tags in the form <at user_id=\"...\">name</at>. Treat these as real mentions of Feishu entities (users or bots).]\n[System: If user_id is \"ou_eaa82a8ab7584770b4b4974610c16e80\", that mention refers to you.]"}],"timestamp":1775083624384}}
{"type":"message","id":"e79449c8","parentId":"7f79ccee","timestamp":"2026-04-01T22:47:17.820Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Prioritizing tasks and fixes**\n\nI need to switch my focus to the new highest priority task. It’s a good idea to note any interruptions and establish a recovery point. I should carry out a code fix and provide evidence of the execution in the same turn, as the user requested. I’ll do the necessary tool calls and consider reading the skill-creator SKILL to ensure I'm on the right track.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0faca0e75e9e48550169cda06ae544819aba20a6109f392efb\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpzaB1dDwbhFhW4H9YDnkS60dnI06ZUN3t1qQeWKQsN5lR_Bs6tbnEkhBD-elf2KhmVzfWwzPO03ZFhSEGowStes-jxHw_qNeDluUZpAjWitA2mi4sc1yU7_tO5xj2qPS64HQkLl8OqCy9wdfkxisaa5Xwh9u5ZQh_4_-uifQwZT5RQ602vNHRRJ9xF1J50voRAJb5PoEdw1RCNPBci5-0YNi6si35AoqvBJEZbPULDO9olN4f2_vLlKIbDj8BhUpmFty_GpegSY90dSpdp3elVxP_zyGmlzdtYOKiWsdQTL6vr1NWMdI-iMutZwmWkgqtYPQKBpYOXVSdiWSkWzWADCuCSvzha4jdVDoOks5n3Ru2HuFO9qXFqYva8ZtdR9iddRV-u4Js2jZTDOXcGKxV31u7F-7mk0wh-n1cMBstSB4WxDpTZbjzUwdE9acs1bXj4EaYPKAh_3_Df5V2eBto5i23HLL8EdkNBN34DvaBqpQ_viEmk290HdNU6loF64L6wxvNGmHWPxTqXd4FfA9VnpvGvVi5-8YtDSnhuBxmUc13fkbM6WFoyH1oZm0KGcop3RF2_F-51XRwtflWqT8hW3RhoIDxECcluBjnxUE3KXwbo8JmEi4esPUumIOH9O4hxbatwjAKW_Kv3F2G9sFuXwJFm1qdjVH3LaJNRXeu3fx6q8Cgb4oeRUz2n_kj4CAkI64_67FynYWOrd0zre7_qFUR1x_ZfyJwfKaFXjeds-WfrH3FndeflTBFO7RQWrZ9lyPGlvYiQQrMk3IMQjFLIKhH57OPrAX9pXWnhHRsRLTxxKi_YGCXcuXwyGJu1EeEvUvtQl33YnZWD63UCS4kY7DmA05QdBfcXVZWb3KhbbKlB0PWN4zyOf8nxt42x9QBX2iIgyRI3bpaoRC-6hDhhwh27gOvjEBBcWDNfFuYu8lCJiiFZ1sgGB5Dqjx2BzlR0gvUTNtGtawRGhRYyMrMz9mPBbzRjSrdsFgwbUwBM5FbzCtEjjiZXoJmTWz0n2PdMPZEirXzAAv5BK0xgqcxHJrEi_vYUpwIuGxdBcuysFPve8-IK1Uwe1vrLdItlRUzvs2vOslaOMysXCCZiFsIIb1hKrn0wqcv09SiwMigfqrQaigirD8ffol-5K31b0frvhhSnJoLz573ZpUuvEaOgB5v2XYRPkQfF5mCFe62Ter94L_68BU0EKKkPGGl-7PS9yiU3gz821apg9nBjhoEauy9NHsKBn5Pa9WqCGr1ygORFg18kZH6_Eyfsuk-8w0p4EcCklFCAXJDXi1V82