ily_stock_analysis` 已经不再会被报成“已最新”，它现在会被识别成**已分叉/需关注**。我再把 fetch 容错收一下，避免某个 remote 失效把整轮检查噪音放大。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0faca0e75e9e48550169cda1e46cc4819a9ade29f3d92622f1\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Improving the fetch script**\n\nI’m thinking we should update the script to handle fetching remotes individually. The current fetch error is significant due to the origin not being found. It makes sense to modify the `fetch_repo` function so that it fetches each remote separately and aggregates errors, yet still succeeds if at least one remote is fetched. However, I have to keep in mind that using `git fetch upstream --prune --tags` could still lead to lock reference errors. I’ll consider using `git remote` to list and fetch each remote.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0faca0e75e9e48550169cda1e4945c819aa08fd0ba9a15e0b2\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpzaHpLsLm_bpcJwQx6RswM23og_M3uz_NEH9fg0Kp5zr0Xwhbx522P4HW7hAg4ZtCq9Z3N5IP4lwoI0MIBHjjNpYhnNIwAiuDwdisbYEYY4qERNahgDuy3bE3GZPWPZlgNr_x9Wtp-i1uL_WvrYZGU7iT5TTGK0XdtzYKOz6eSfDrqwIrV80RBdMOpwGulHD_gCj9Yg1bepyefsvkyuu1_12B4yZ5oDzA2Vz5w2iKUAeAoZHlxa_w7-s49lgb9qfiizZOvoTDLttMsh4jeMeT1HaueKDERhcDw3Hrs5YOX_EcIJB554-xs-c_8kuQNqMzAsT_6fIeZL_gJ17C85zyUyPDnSwyEOPnuHewxAgIkLU9yewR_bl-vVyfk4rBbzEF2lsfYULFVXa4R4WEJUa1MEvCeWbfZfiiWY-GHW11HbMlA34XgB09itbji2_NG8hgAEciMNVcN2G37wuOeNT3iY4ZYyr94CLBSlu16qNEpwoN25CjJRC9h7d_mgEkNyk5AgdrEaY_uRuL0XzE_onCU0OwOpLwGDqV1Z4PUSyKcA74yN2nt0EGEvcC77VjtGjXDwRLW_WpthumsOOXw-RZuE3BRGDwzL2foq7tSju6n76xyl_TF24uUzPCGm6sb2gWXSNZv31Qw4_eP8zQdi2a7O3_hgr3743MfLGQrTa8fn2JQhuTBpbjqMJZMObn691ulQgLR6k4CUctCQb4G-dRvi9A2iVb-AcP0jvM_gyiv6QATC4L0O2vr0qBF5yRZhWO0r1vPE-RN3XKY6BvbyporZqEKvxMBL1xL084VGeWZDEBzedkzTBDDpb_G5vh3zZ56ywfu58CTFC9S2JBJMBb7UCDk9j9x88B85YJW8AJWtRbOCuvcJq75ge7Z0XJOpEtno9EymX4TFdM5Ry74MbmVJfgccsoWatKfSDZ71dATpLIqYrcZjqPV44iceVepumckMw3sGL4xKFd-2r4odoBa-_iNblLd7O3P-yVeeydfQPGphY4Lc-x6c3rNZkYJm_XdKgbuI3NYazbdPPgwsYur12fqsrrlkErSldCz7KP