{"type":"message","id":"218d2bbb","parentId":"79c9ab23","timestamp":"2026-04-01T22:59:07.365Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_WMNcBirhqxiQGR7IG5U1UDEh|fc_0faca0e75e9e48550169cda3306be0819abb9675bf52b3a6f1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Status: active\nPriority: P0\nStarted: 2026-04-02 06:48\nUpdated: 2026-04-02 06:48\nWorkspace: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\nOwner: main-session\nUser Trigger: 张玲在飞书群明确指令“你直接修复 coding agent”\nResume Entry: /Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/scripts/check_updates.py\n\n## Goal\n- 修复 github-repo-monitor 的误报口径，避免把“本地已有更新/工作区有变化”的仓库继续报成“已最新/无需更新”\n\n## Acceptance\n- 脚本可被宿主 `python3` 成功编译\n- `daily_stock_analysis` 不再被摘要误报为“已最新 / 无需更新”\n- 报告/摘要至少能区分：上游待更新、本地有变化、已同步\n\n## Current\n- 继续补做整批 4 仓库验收，确认新摘要口径在全量检查下稳定\n\n## Next\n- 输出 4 仓库全量状态样例\n- 如无异常，归档本轮修复结果并结束任务\n- 恢复此前被插单的微博抓取链路修复：`research/reports/weibo_mcp_auth_blocker_20260402.md`\n\n## Completed\n- [2026-04-02 06:45] 已直接修改 `~/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/scripts/check_updates.py`\n- [2026-04-02 06:45] 已把监控口径从“只看是否落后上游”改为区分：上游待更新 / 本地已有变化 / 工作区改动 / 已同步\n- [2026-04-02 06:46] 已加入 fetch 刷新远端引用，避免只对比陈旧 remote-tracking refs\n- [2026-04-02 06:47] 已修复 Python 3.9 兼容性问题（去掉 `str | None` 注解写法）\n- [2026-04-02 06:47] 已完成语法验收：`python3 -m py_compile ~/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/scripts/check_updates.py` -> `PY_COMPILE_OK`\n- [2026-04-02 06:48] 已完成单仓验收：`daily_stock_analysis` 的新摘要变为“🛠️ GitHub 仓库检查 | 上游无需更新 | 本地有变化 1 | 已同步 0 / 本地变化：daily_stock_analysis”\n\n## Evidence\n- 文件：`/Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/scripts/check_updates.py`\n- 命令：`python3 -m py_compile /Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/scripts/check_updates.py` -> `PY_COMPILE_OK`\n- 命令：本地导入脚本并检查 `daily_stock_analysis` -> 新摘要不再是“已最新 / 无需更新”\n- 微博修复恢复点：`/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/weibo_mcp_auth_blocker_20260402.md`\n\n## Blockers\n- 全量 4 仓库验收仍在跑 `git fetch`，需要等待最后一轮本地验证完成\n\n## Rules\n- `Current` must contain exactly one active item.\n- After finishing `Current`, move it to `Completed`, add proof under `Evidence`, then promote the first item in `Next` into `Current`.\n- Prefer rewriting the whole file once instead of chaining multiple partial edits.\n- After each write, read the file back and verify `Current`, `Next`, and `Completed` before reporting the new state.\n- If prompt context reports `Integrity Warnings`, repair the file before claiming the task state changed.\n- Only set `Status: blocked` when the blocker is real and specific.\n- Only set `Status: done` when `Acceptance` is met.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775084347359}}
