6-04-02 新生成的 holdings 主源文件，说明“上午纠正”大概率未真正写回 selected holdings 主链\n\n## Evidence\n- `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/selected_real_holdings_source_latest.json`\n- `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/holdings_sync_guard_latest.md`\n- `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/config/ths_local_holdings_selection.json`\n- 命令：`python3 ~/.openclaw/skills/ths-local-holdings/scripts/ths_local_holdings.py list`\n- 命令：`find ... -newermt '2026-04-02 00:00:00'` 未发现新的 holdings 主源文件\n\n## Blockers\n- 上午纠正所依据的原始主源材料（网页 API、HAR、cURL、显式 ledger 选择）尚未在当前链路中看到落盘证据；若没有新的主源输入，系统只能继续沿用昨日 23 只快照\n\n## Rules\n- `Current` must contain exactly one active item.\n- After finishing `Current`, move it to `Completed`, add proof under `Evidence`, then promote the first item in `Next` into `Current`.\n- Prefer rewriting the whole file once instead of chaining multiple partial edits.\n- After each write, read the file back and verify `Current`, `Next`, and `Completed` before reporting the new state.\n- If prompt context reports `Integrity Warnings`, repair the file before claiming the task state changed.\n- Only set `Status: blocked` when the blocker is real and specific.\n- Only set `Status: done` when `Acceptance` is met.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775084650136}}
