":"[[reply_to_current]] 收到，我继续补监控清单。\n\n接下来我会直接做两步：\n1. 把漏掉的仓库补进监控配置\n2. 按 **主仓 / 预览仓 / skill 仓 / vendor 仓** 分组，避免后面报告混在一起\n\n改完我直接把：\n- 新纳入的仓库名单\n- 排除名单\n- 最终监控总数\n\n一起回给你。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0faca0e75e9e48550169cda68c26a0819a8061011eeb22e612\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":132834,"output":239,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":133073,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775085156112,"responseId":"resp_0faca0e75e9e48550169cda685c8c4819a8ded37169e8e87d0"}}
