{"type":"message","id":"f3d5200f","parentId":"3157674a","timestamp":"2026-04-01T23:22:06.379Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 报告已出，先给你结论和路径。\n\n**报告文件**\n- `research/reports/holdings_chain_root_cause_report_20260402.md`\n\n**当前阶段**\n- 已定位主根因\n- 还**没完全修完**\n- 当前最小阻断点：**没有新的、已落盘并被主链接管的真实持仓主源**\n\n**关键指标**\n1. 当前主源仍是旧快照\n   - `selected_real_holdings_source_latest.json`\n   - 生成时间：`2026-04-01 19:19:39`\n   - 来源：`web`\n   - 持仓数：`23`\n\n2. 同步守卫也还在用旧口径\n   - `holdings_sync_guard_latest.md`\n   - 使用持仓数：`23`\n\n3. 选择配置没有绑明确 ledger\n   - `ths_local_holdings_selection.json`\n   - `selected_ledger_ids=[]`\n   - 仍以旧 web selected holdings 为主源\n\n4. 本地实际有多套账本\n   - 我已实查到 3 个候选 ledger\n   - 不是单一口径，不能靠猜\n\n5. 今天发现的新 holdings 文件\n   - 主要是 `paper/execution holdings`\n   - **不是** selected holdings 主源\n   - 说明“上午纠正”没有真正写回主链\n\n**一句话结论**\n- 问题不是“消息层没刷新”这么简单\n- 而是**真实持仓主链仍绑定昨天的 23 只旧 web 快照**\n- 所以上午纠正后，后续链路还会继续发旧持仓\n\n**我现在继续做的下一步**\n- 继续找上午纠正时到底用了哪份主源材料\n- 优先查：网页 API / HAR / cURL / ledger 证据\n- 一旦找到，就直接重建：\n  - `ths_web_selected_holdings_latest.*`\n  - `selected_real_holdings_source_latest.json`\n\n如果你现在就要看完整文字版，直接看这个文件：\n- `research/reports/holdings_chain_root_cause_report_20260402.md`","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0faca0e75e9e48550169cda8951420819aad90639f1ff6c059\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1152,"output":486,"cacheRead":130560,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":132198,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775085714551,"responseId":"resp_0faca0e75e9e48550169cda8939274819aa47cd376e516d7ee"}}
