{"type":"message","id":"e36fc917","parentId":"bc3a611b","timestamp":"2026-04-01T23:25:10.331Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 报告已出。\n\n**报告文件**\n- `research/reports/buy_candidates_refresh_report_20260402.md`\n\n**当前阶段**\n- 已拿到强证据\n- 还**没修完**\n- 当前最小结论：**截至我检查时，今天没有新的 `20260402` 候选链产物落盘，系统仍在沿用 `20260401` 的最新候选证据**\n\n**关键证据**\n1. 守卫规则还没完全修好\n   - `quant_p0_p1_guard_rules_v1.json`\n   - `P0-004`\n   - 状态：`partial`\n   - 含义：盘中/下午自动重跑仍有复用上午或昨日产物的风险\n\n2. 我没查到新的 `20260402` 候选链文件\n   - 检查范围包括：\n     - `candidate`\n     - `signal_tickets`\n     - `approved_signals`\n     - `proposed_orders`\n   - 结果：**未发现 20260402 新文件**\n\n3. 目前最新一批相关产物还是 `20260401`\n   - 例如：\n     - `paper_aggressive_signal_tickets_20260401.csv`\n     - `paper_balanced_signal_tickets_20260401.csv`\n     - `paper_defensive_signal_tickets_20260401.csv`\n     - `paper_*_merged_approved_signals_20260401.csv`\n     - `paper_*_merged_proposed_orders_20260401.csv`\n     - `paper_*_smallcap_candidate_generation_20260401.json`\n\n**一句话结论**\n- 你说“今天的买入候选跟昨天一样，没有更新吗”\n- **当前证据支持这个判断**\n- 不是你看错了，而是**今天这条候选刷新链截至检查时确实还没产出新的 20260402 结果**\n\n如果你要，我下一步就继续顺着这条链去抓：\n- 今天到底有没有真正触发重跑\n- 如果触发了，是卡在候选生成、signal tickets，还是 latest 引用没有切换","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0faca0e75e9e48550169cda94d673c819aa99eb58816e332fc\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":92614,"output":471,"cacheRead":36352,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":129437,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775085872463,"responseId":"resp_0faca0e75e9e48550169cda94b2d58819a9960e469641ba3a9"}}
{"type":"message","id":"25c83ee0","parentId":"e36fc917","timestamp":"2026-04-01T23:25:51.257Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b53eed9195ca0b387000a4eb6456\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"om_x100b53edaeec5934c36ed648b927c63\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_8a819be3a90d35b8d0a2d5c1f4642b22\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-04-02 07:25 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_8a819be3a90d35b8d0a2d5c1f4642b22\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"body\": \"@_user_1 @_user_2 为什么有些仓库明明就更新了，你还监测不到？这个skill是不是有问题？例如，我今天手动更新了daily_stock_analysis\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b53eed9195ca0b387000a4eb6456]\n张玲: [Replying to: \"@_user_1 @_user_2 为什么有些仓库明明就更新了，你还监测不到？这个skill是不是有问题？例如，我今天手动更新了daily_stock_analysis\"]\n\n你把全量的仓库都加入扫描的名单，每天报告是否有更新"}],"timestamp":1775085951250}}
