N3zSjpUkcZDgbwALE94_TCgZL-nKjhvFL44p6nj2rN7HRHHvgLkiX7yPkIc=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Inspecting repository settings**\\n\\nI’m considering whether I really need more guidance or if I should focus on the task at hand. The user asked me to add all repositories to scan daily, which could be sensitive as it might modify configurations and scheduling. I think I can proceed without needing explicit confirmation since it’s internal. Now, I need to look into the skill directory for the configuration or script schedule, so let’s inspect the github-repo-monitor skill files.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"我先补配置和调度现状，确认是“只改清单”还是还要补每天的触发。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0faca0e75e9e48550169cda9a605ec819ab3116bb57aa442c2\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3KCyug4Vhl5tjpqta2I7J9wN|fc_0faca0e75e9e48550169cda9a7ada0819ab2acec62152ea451","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor -maxdepth 3 -type f | sed 's#^#FILE #' | sort","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":40},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"find /Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor -maxdepth 3 -type f | sed 's#^#FILE #' | sort\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\",\"timeout\":40}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4E1KcL3qSQYz7ra0ktHikHTd|fc_0faca0e75e9e48550169cda9a7adb4819aae798089bdaa592f","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/SKILL.md","limit":220},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/SKILL.md\",\"limit\":220}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6tv1fCu1RxUBUmdutlJabuew|fc_0faca0e75e9e48550169cda9a7adbc819a979125179dec6890","name":"read","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/config/repos.json","limit":240},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/config/repos.json\",\"limit\":240}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":128192,"output":248,"cacheRead":8704,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":137144,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775085969122,"responseId":"resp_0faca0e75e9e48550169cda9a0176c819a96fced383c3f9ffd"}}
{"type":"message","id":"25df8799","parentId":"b5a68a9c","timestamp":"2026-04-01T23:26:33.647Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_3KCyug4Vhl5tjpqta2I7J9wN|fc_0faca0e75e9e48550169cda9a7ada0819ab2acec62152ea451","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"FILE /Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/SKILL.md\nFILE /Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/config/repos.json\nFILE /Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/logs/check_updates.err\nFILE /Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/logs/check_updates.log\nFILE /Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/scripts/check_updates.py\nFILE /Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/state/last_check.json"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":9,"aggregated":"FILE /Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/SKILL.md\nFILE /Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/config/repos.json\nFILE /Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/logs/check_updates.err\nFILE /Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/logs/check_updates.log\nFILE /Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/scripts/check_updates.py\nFILE /Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/state/last_check.json","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775085993641}}
{"type":"message","id":"f2353651","parentId":"25df8799","timestamp":"2026-04-01T23:26:33.651Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_4E1KcL3qSQYz7ra0ktHikHTd|fc_0faca0e75e9e48550169cda9a7adb4819aae798089bdaa592f","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# GitHub Repo Monitor Skill\n\n自动追踪指定 GitHub 仓库的更新情况，分析 changelog 并判断是否应更新本地副本。\n\n## 功能\n\n| 功能 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 🔍 上游更新检测 | 检查 upstream remote 与本地的 commit 差距 |\n| 📊 优先级分类 | 按 feat/fix/refactor/breaking 打标签 |\n| 🧠 智能建议 | 自动判断是否建议更新本地仓库 |\n| 📲 飞书通知 | 有重要更新时推送摘要到飞书 |\n| 📝 报告存档 | 输出 Markdown + JSON 状态文件 |\n\n## 监控范围\n\n自动发现并监控以下仓库：\n- `daily_stock_analysis`（上游 ZhuLinsen）\n- `qlib`（上游 seablue1985）\n- 其他带 upstream remote 的 Git 仓库\n\n## 配置\n\n编辑 `config/repos.json` 添加/删除仓库：\n\n```json\n[\n  {\"path\": \"/path/to/repo1\"},\n  {\"path\": \"/path/to/repo2\"}\n]\n```\n\n留空则自动发现 workspace 下所有有 upstream 的仓库。\n\n## 使用方法\n\n### 手动检查\n```bash\n/usr/local/bin/python3 /Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/scripts/check_updates.py\n```\n\n### 定时自动\nLaunchAgent 已配置，每日 09:00 / 21:00 自动检查。\n\n```bash\n# 查看日志\ncat ~/Library/Logs/github-repo-monitor.log\n\n# 重启服务\nlaunchctl unload ~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.ling.github-repo-monitor.plist\nlaunchctl load ~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.ling.github-repo-monitor.plist\n```\n\n## 报告示例\n\n```\n# GitHub 仓库更新报告 — 2026-03-22\n\n**检查仓库数：8 | 建议更新：2 | 已最新：5**\n\n## 🔔 需要关注的更新\n\n### daily_stock_analysis ⭐⭐⭐（v3.9.0）\n- 当前版本：v3.4.8\n- 上游版本：v3.9.0\n- 落后：20 commits | Ahead：0\n- **建议：落后 20 个 commits，建议一次性合并**\n- 包含：Slack通知、REPORT_LANGUAGE配置、TickFlow行情、AutoComplete\n\n## ✅ 所有仓库已最新，无需更新\n```\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775085993647}}
