I2q0eZPA6ArKF-07qX8q1MUlRXWRcslyJ2Hkiw57Sgh\",\"summary\":[]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 收到。**主需求已经修完了**，结论直接给你：\n\n### 已修完的部分\n1. **全量仓库已加入扫描名单**\n   - 当前清单：`22` 个仓库\n   - 配置文件：`~/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/config/repos.json`\n\n2. **每天自动报告已确认可用**\n   - LaunchAgent：`com.ling.github-repo-monitor`\n   - 调度时间：**每日 09:00**\n   - 文件：`~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.ling.github-repo-monitor.plist`\n\n3. **首轮全量扫描已经跑完**\n   - 最新报告：`research/reports/github_repo_update_report_20260402.md`\n   - 最新状态：`research/reports/github_repo_update_state_20260402.json`\n   - 清单验收：`research/reports/github_repo_monitor_inventory_20260402.md`\n\n### 本轮首扫结果\n- 检查仓库数：`22`\n- 上游待更新：`15`\n- 本地有变化：`13`\n- 已同步：`3`\n\n### 所以现在的状态\n- **“只有 4 个仓库被监控”这个问题：已修完**\n- **“每天报告是否有更新”这个能力：已修完**\n- **“daily_stock_analysis 明明更新了却监测不到”这个误报口径：已修完**\n\n### 还没做、但不影响主需求交付的\n- **报告降噪/分层** 还没做  \n  现在预览仓、upstream 仓、skill/vendor 仓也会一起报，所以信息会偏杂。  \n  这属于**优化项，不是主需求阻断**。\n\n如果你要，我下一步就做降噪版，把日报拆成：\n- 主仓\n- 扩展仓\n- 预览/镜像仓","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0faca0e75e9e48550169cdb475ea80819a8d6d6c164a3e3f7f\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":135186,"output":576,"cacheRead":5632,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":141394,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775088749939,"responseId":"resp_0faca0e75e9e48550169cdb46f76bc819a9b258b04fe62850f"}}
