{"type":"message","id":"46a73852","parentId":"23d2f28c","timestamp":"2026-04-02T04:44:34.891Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_MMcOVcc7xV48EyjMONfQQ5fA|fc_0faca0e75e9e48550169cdf4315ab4819a86480900605b1a3c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Status: done\nPriority: P0\nStarted: 2026-04-02 12:43\nUpdated: 2026-04-02 12:45\nWorkspace: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\nOwner: main-session\nUser Trigger: 张玲要求仓库日报排除 `daily_stock_analysis_upgrade_preview` / `daily_stock_analysis_upstream`，并在“上游已更新、本地没更新”时明确给出“是否值得更新”的判断\nResume Entry: /Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/scripts/check_updates.py\n\n## Goal\n- 调整 github-repo-monitor 报告口径：排除两个 daily_stock_analysis 派生仓，并在上游待更新项中明确输出“更新判断”\n\n## Acceptance\n- `repos.json` 中这两个派生仓不会再被自动发现重新加回\n- 监控仓库数从 22 降到 20\n- 报告/摘要对上游待更新项明确输出“更新判断”文案\n\n## Current\n- 无；本轮验收已完成\n\n## Next\n- 如张玲确认需要，再继续做“主仓/扩展仓/预览镜像仓”分层降噪优化\n\n## Completed\n- [2026-04-02 12:42] 已重写 `~/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/scripts/check_updates.py`，支持 `enabled:false` 排除仓库，且把“建议”改成“更新判断”\n- [2026-04-02 12:43] 已在 `~/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/config/repos.json` 中把 `daily_stock_analysis_upstream` / `daily_stock_analysis_upgrade_preview` 标记为 `enabled:false`\n- [2026-04-02 12:44] 已通过语法验收：`python3 -m py_compile ~/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/scripts/check_updates.py` -> `PY_COMPILE_OK`\n- [2026-04-02 12:44] 已通过配置验收：`load_config()` 返回 `REPO_COUNT 20`，且两个派生仓 `INCLUDED=False`\n- [2026-04-02 12:44] 已通过摘要验收：`build_summary()` 输出新增 `判断：值得更新：...` 文案\n\n## Evidence\n- `/Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/scripts/check_updates.py`\n- `/Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/config/repos.json`\n- `python3 -m py_compile /Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/github-repo-monitor/scripts/check_updates.py` -> `PY_COMPILE_OK`\n- `python3 - <<'PY' ... load_config() ... PY` -> `REPO_COUNT 20`\n- `python3 - <<'PY' ... build_summary(codexpool) ... PY` -> `判断：值得更新：包含 Breaking Changes，需优先评估并安排更新（8 commits）`\n\n## Blockers\n- None\n\n## Rules\n- `Current` must contain exactly one active item.\n- After finishing `Current`, move it to `Completed`, add proof under `Evidence`, then promote the first item in `Next` into `Current`.\n- Prefer rewriting the whole file once instead of chaining multiple partial edits.\n- After each write, read the file back and verify `Current`, `Next`, and `Completed` before reporting the new state.\n- If prompt context reports `Integrity Warnings`, repair the file before claiming the task state changed.\n- Only set `Status: blocked` when the blocker is real and specific.\n- Only set `Status: done` when `Acceptance` is met.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775105074869}}
