{"type":"message","id":"1093a241","parentId":"3f320b37","timestamp":"2026-04-02T06:42:34.690Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The file only has 6 lines - header + 5 data rows. That's a pretty small file. Let me check if there are bigger files with actual candidate content.\n\nActually, the key finding here is:\n1. There ARE 20260402 files (so the system DID run today)\n2. The files have real 2026-04-02 data with timestamps like `2026-04-02T09:46:34`\n3. But the files are SMALL - defensive signal_tickets has only 6 lines\n\nThis means: the system DID run today and generated new artifacts, but the content may be sparse/thin. This could explain why the user feels \"buyers are the same as yesterday\" - the new artifacts may have very few entries or the same entries as yesterday.","thinkingSignature":"1839ab1e923804bd5932f6fe4a20f9ca418bd73476b548f66fd3b06c9fc005fd"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 核查完毕，结论直接说：\n\n**今天候选链确实跑了，不是完全没更新。**\n\n关键证据：\n- 今天（04-02）已落盘的候选/信号文件共有 **37 个**，覆盖：\n  - `paper_defensive_signal_tickets_20260402.csv`\n  - `paper_balanced_merged_approved_signals_20260402.csv`\n  - `live_smallcap_candidate_generation_20260402.json`\n  - `paper_*_smallcap_*_20260402.csv` 等\n\n- 数据里已有真实 04-02 时间戳，例如：\n  - `generated_at: 2026-04-02T09:46:34`\n\n**但文件比较小**，例如 `paper_defensive_signal_tickets_20260402.csv` 只有 6 行（1 表头 + 5 实际数据）。\n\n**所以你感觉\"候选跟昨天差不多\"，可能是因为：**\n1. 今天新生成的候选数量本身就很有限\n2. 三套模拟盘里，可能只有少数票真正通过了今天的信号审核\n\n如果你要进一步看**今天具体是哪几只票进了买入候选**，我可以把今天 04-02 的 `approved_signals` 和 `proposed_orders` 里的票名列出来，直接给你看。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":131287,"output":434,"cacheRead":25640,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":157361,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775112131122,"responseId":"061d42c3f5d7f9608322643e2a8e30f8"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0abd5a60","parentId":"1093a241","timestamp":"2026-04-02T06:49:59.953Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b53d557ac2cb4c101a2bb3efb73c\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"om_x100b5381f30b38a4c4abae1224052db\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_8a819be3a90d35b8d0a2d5c1f4642b22\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-04-02 14:49 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_8a819be3a90d35b8d0a2d5c1f4642b22\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"body\": \"@_user_1 @_user_2 今天的买入候选跟昨天是一样的，没有更新吗\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b53d557ac2cb4c101a2bb3efb73c]\n张玲: [Replying to: \"@_user_1 @_user_2 今天的买入候选跟昨天是一样的，没有更新吗\"]\n\n好"}],"timestamp":1775112599938}}
{"type":"message","id":"e66cf574","parentId":"0abd5a60","timestamp":"2026-04-02T06:50:27.603Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user said \"好\" in response to my previous message where I offered to list the specific stocks that entered buy candidates today. They agreed. Let me actually do it - list the specific stocks from today's approved_signals and proposed_orders files.\n\nLet me read the key files to extract the actual stock codes.","thinkingSignature":"b3b8db8208f9a5ade7f667afb752c3fd04bcdca28c088790a0566581c3c1ccd8"},{"type":"text","text":"\n收到，我来把今天（04-02）具体进了买入候选的票列出来。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wczm8budm084_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 - <<'PY'\nfrom pathlib import Path\nimport json\n\nreports = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports')\n\n# 三套盘的 approved_signals 和 proposed_orders\npairs = [\n    ('paper_aggressive_merged_approved_signals_20260402.csv', 'paper_aggressive_merged_proposed_orders_20260402.csv'),\n    ('paper_balanced_merged_approved_signals_20260402.csv', 'paper_balanced_merged_proposed_orders_20260402.csv'),\n    ('paper_defensive_merged_approved_signals_20260402.csv', 'paper_defensive_merged_proposed_orders_20260402.csv'),\n]\n\nfor approved_f, proposed_f in pairs:\n    ap = reports / approved_f\n    pr = reports / proposed_f\n    plate = approved_f.split('_')[1].capitalize()\n\n    approved_stocks = []\n    if ap.exists():\n        lines = [l.strip() for l in ap.read_text(errors='ignore').splitlines() if l.strip()]\n        if len(lines) > 1:\n            header = lines[0].lower()\n            # find ts_code / symbol column\n            cols = header.split(',')\n            tc_col = next((i for i,c in enumerate(cols) if 'ts_code' in c or 'code' in c or 'symbol' in c), 1)\n            approved_stocks = [lines[i].split(',')[tc_col] for i in range(1, len(lines))]\n\n    proposed_stocks = []\n    if pr.exists():\n        lines = [l.strip() for l in pr.read_text(errors='ignore').splitlines() if l.strip()]\n        if len(lines) > 1:\n            cols = lines[0].lower()\n            tc_col = next((i for i,c in enumerate(cols.split(',')) if 'ts_code' in c or 'code' in c or 'symbol' in c), 1)\n            proposed_stocks = [lines[i].split(',')[tc_col] for i in range(1, len(lines))]\n\n    print(f'\\n=== {plate}盘 ===')\n    print(f'  Approved: {approved_stocks or \"(空)\"}')\n    print(f'  Proposed: {proposed_stocks or \"(空)\"}')\n\n# 也看看 signal_tickets（实际触发交易的票）\nprint('\\n=== 今日触发票（signal_tickets）===')\nfor f in sorted(reports.glob('*signal_tickets_20260402*')):\n    lines = [l.strip() for l in f.read_text(errors='ignore').splitlines() if l.strip()]\n    if len(lines) > 1:\n        cols = lines[0].lower()\n        ts_col = next((i for i,c in enumerate(cols.split(',')) if 'ts_code' in c or 'code' in c), 1)\n        stocks = [lines[i].split(',')[ts_col] for i in range(1, len(lines))]\n        print(f'  {f.name}: {stocks}')\nPY","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":74,"output":786,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":159864,"totalTokens":160724,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775112599951,"responseId":"061d44986098c57860e31edd6cedd007"}}
