{"type":"message","id":"0cbd72e1","parentId":"c0d3de64","timestamp":"2026-04-02T06:50:51.198Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the actual stock codes for today's candidates. Let me present this clearly.\n\nKey findings:\n- Aggressive盘: 空（没有 approved/proposed stocks）\n- Balanced盘: 11 只票 approved/proposed - 但 wait, the user said \"买入候选跟昨天一样\" - let me check if these are the same as yesterday\n- Defensive盘: 5 只票 approved/proposed\n\nThe signal_tickets for Defensive shows 002025.XSHE as a SELL signal (exit due to stop_loss_reduce), while the others are BUY signals.\n\nFor Balanced盘, the approved stocks are: 002025.SZ, 002112.SZ, 002222.SZ, 002342.SZ, 002361.SZ, 300063.SZ, 300503.SZ, 300775.SZ, 300900.SZ, 301005.SZ, 688387.SH\n\n\nI need to compare these lists against yesterday's approved and proposed stocks to see if there's been any turnover.","thinkingSignature":"0e8f5c07adb44f183a13a77189e774420fdbcc75c2d5bfc144e52ba716c94379"},{"type":"text","text":"今天有真实数据进来。我再顺查一下和昨天（04-01）对比，看是不是真的重复了。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qfp9juj0ztri_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 - <<'PY'\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nreports = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports')\n\npairs = [\n    ('paper_aggressive_merged_approved_signals_20260401.csv', 'paper_balanced_merged_approved_signals_20260401.csv', 'paper_defensive_merged_approved_signals_20260401.csv'),\n]\n\nfor af1, af2, af3 in pairs:\n    for f in [af1, af2, af3]:\n        fp = reports / f\n        if not fp.exists():\n            continue\n        lines = [l.strip() for l in fp.read_text(errors='ignore').splitlines() if l.strip()]\n        if len(lines) <= 1:\n            continue\n        cols = lines[0].lower().split(',')\n        tc_col = next((i for i,c in enumerate(cols) if 'ts_code' in c or 'code' in c or 'symbol' in c), 1)\n        stocks = sorted(set(lines[i].split(',')[tc_col] for i in range(1, len(lines))))\n        plate = f.split('_')[1].capitalize()\n        print(f'{plate} yesterday ({f}): {stocks}')\n\n# today's balanced for comparison\nfp2 = reports / 'paper_balanced_merged_approved_signals_20260402.csv'\nlines2 = [l.strip() for l in fp2.read_text(errors='ignore').splitlines() if l.strip()]\ncols2 = lines2[0].lower().split(',')\ntc_col2 = next((i for i,c in enumerate(cols2) if 'ts_code' in c or 'code' in c or 'symbol' in c), 1)\nstocks2 = sorted(set(lines2[i].split(',')[tc_col2] for i in range(1, len(lines2))))\nprint(f'\\nBalanced TODAY (20260402): {stocks2}')\nPY","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":134156,"output":709,"cacheRead":25640,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":160505,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775112627713,"responseId":"061d44b3e1d97b55b7c4aa7a38abe245"}}
