{"type":"message","id":"6c3baea4","parentId":"9ccf0790","timestamp":"2026-04-02T06:58:17.211Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see something very important! Let me check:\n\n- `runtime_risk_state_latest.json` - updated 14:20 today (04-02)\n- `runtime_risk_state_latest_defensive.json` - updated 06:41 on 04-01 (yesterday!)\n- `runtime_risk_state_latest_balanced.json` - updated 06:41 on 04-01 (yesterday!)\n\nSo the defensive盘's runtime state file is from yesterday morning (04-01 06:41), not today! This means the defensive盘's pre-check/risk state is stale.\n \nThe real problem is that the defensive盘的 prewrite file was generated from yesterday's runtime state, which explains why the approved signals are identical to yesterday's results. The pipeline appears to be running with stale runtime data instead of today's state, likely because the auto-premarket check didn't run or update properly today. I need to look at the `auto_premarket_precheck_20260402.json` file to understand what actually triggered the run.\n\nLooking at the candidate generation, both days used the same smallcap stocks from the live system, but the defensive盘's runtime state is frozen from yesterday at 06:41. I should check if the live_system_v1_report from today shows any differences in the selected holdings, or if the holdings source is still pointing to yesterday's snapshot.","thinkingSignature":"9d0dadc37679ad64b0e348958ade7cf960a4751c61eba041546463238fb4a08e"},{"type":"text","text":"发现关键线索——防御盘的 runtime state 文件是昨天早上 06:41 的，不是今天的。我继续追。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jzdzn8zoo957_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 - <<'PY'\nfrom pathlib import Path\nimport json, datetime\n\nreports = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports')\n\nkey_files = {\n    'runtime_risk_state_latest': reports / 'runtime_risk_state_latest.json',\n    'runtime_defensive': reports / 'runtime_risk_state_latest_defensive.json',\n    'runtime_balanced': reports / 'runtime_risk_state_latest_balanced.json',\n    'prewrite_defensive_20260402': reports / 'prewrite_paper_guard_defensive_20260402.json',\n    'live_sys_20260402': reports / 'live_system_v1_20260402.json',\n}\nfor name, fp in key_files.items():\n    if fp.exists():\n        mtime = datetime.datetime.fromtimestamp(fp.stat().st_mtime).strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M')\n        size = fp.stat().st_size\n        # read key fields\n        try:\n            data = json.loads(fp.read_text(encoding='utf-8', errors='ignore'))\n            if isinstance(data, dict):\n                keys = list(data.keys())[:6]\n                print(f'\\n{name}: mtime={mtime} size={size}')\n                print(f'  top_keys={keys}')\n                # show trading_status / halt info\n                ts = data.get('trading_status') or data.get('execution_layer',{}).get('trading_status') if isinstance(data,dict) else None\n                if ts:\n                    print(f'  trading_status={ts}')\n            else:\n                print(f'\\n{name}: mtime={mtime} size={size} type={type(data).__name__}')\n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f'\\n{name}: mtime={mtime} size={size} read_err={e}')\n    else:\n        print(f'\\n{name}: NOT FOUND')\nPY","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":132503,"output":766,"cacheRead":25640,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":158909,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775113069358,"responseId":"061d466dd3529ad02515742ff2e860db"}}
