{"type":"message","id":"a757b732","parentId":"23281a72","timestamp":"2026-04-02T06:58:33.144Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Very interesting! Now I see:- `runtime_defensive.json` - from 04-01 06:41 (yesterday morning)- `runtime_balanced.json` - from 04-01 06:41 (yesterday morning)\n- But `runtime_risk_state_latest.json` is from today 04-02 14:20\n\nAnd `prewrite_paper_guard_defensive_20260402.json` was generated today at 09:45 using the stale defensive runtime state from yesterday.\n\nSo the issue is clear: the defensive盘的 `runtime_risk_state_latest_defensive.json` is from yesterday morning (04-01 06:41), and the today's candidate generation used that stale state file.\n \nThe prewrite guard was rebuilt today at 09:45 but it's still pulling from that outdated defensive state, so the candidates end up identical to yesterday's. Now I need to trace back where `runtime_risk_state_latest_defensive.json` originates to understand why it hasn't been refreshed.","thinkingSignature":"cc5fb9613d456817139445c9cb7270a9d02b98da208472b7a9afdc146b76c7c3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fwivepd76w4a_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 - <<'PY'\nfrom pathlib import Path\nimport json, datetime\n\nreports = Path('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports')\n\n# 看 defensive runtime state 的 generated_at 和 date_tag\nfor fname in ['runtime_risk_state_latest_defensive.json', 'runtime_risk_state_latest_balanced.json', 'runtime_risk_state_latest.json']:\n    fp = reports / fname\n    if fp.exists():\n        data = json.loads(fp.read_text(encoding='utf-8', errors='ignore'))\n        gen_at = data.get('generated_at', '?')\n        date_tag = data.get('date_tag', '?')\n        ts = data.get('execution_layer', {}).get('trading_status') if isinstance(data.get('execution_layer'), dict) else '?'\n        print(f'{fname}:')\n        print(f'  generated_at={gen_at}')\n        print(f'  date_tag={date_tag}')\n        print(f'  trading_status={ts}')\n\n# 看 prewrite guard 引用的是哪个 runtime_state_file\nfp2 = reports / 'prewrite_paper_guard_defensive_20260402.json'\nif fp2.exists():\n    data2 = json.loads(fp2.read_text(encoding='utf-8', errors='ignore'))\n    print(f'\\nprewrite_defensive_20260402:')\n    print(f'  runtime_state_file={data2.get(\"runtime_state_file\",\"?\")}')\n    print(f'  runtime_date_tag={data2.get(\"runtime_date_tag\",\"?\")}')\nPY","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":133538,"output":592,"cacheRead":25640,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":159770,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775113097321,"responseId":"061d4689813f0cf644aa028cb7480ff4"}}
