{"type":"message","id":"72932af4","parentId":"b1543b40","timestamp":"2026-04-02T07:08:39.150Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_bctiw52q6yt3_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-04-02\n\n## 持续有效的系统结论\n- `github-repo-monitor` 旧口径存在误报：此前只看 `commits_behind`，把“本地已新增 / ahead>0”的仓库误报为“已最新”；修复方向已明确为：检查前先 `git fetch`，并区分 `上游待更新 / 本地有变化 / 工作区改动 / 已同步`，不能再把 `ahead>0` 视为“无变化”。\n- `daily_stock_analysis` 是该误报的已验证样例：本地相对远端存在明显 ahead，但旧摘要仍报“4 个已最新 | 无需更新”；后续若再看仓库监控结果，必须防止把“未落后”误读成“没有更新”。\n\n## 微博监控稳定结论\n- “微博财经大V每日简报”此前的过滤问题已修掉（不再按 `is_stock_related` / `FINANCE_KEYWORDS` 先筛再报），但当前真正阻断抓取的是微博登录态失效，不是过滤逻辑。\n- 已验证的底层阻断：`mcp-server-weibo` 的访客 Cookie 会被微博打到验证码页（`ok=-100`），而 skill 中现有 `WEIBO_COOKIE` 也已失效并跳回登录页；在没有新的有效 `WEIBO_COOKIE` 前，日报继续出现“抓取 0 条微博”属于登录态问题，不是分析层问题。\n\n## 持仓链路当前真实状态\n- 当前 selected holdings 主链仍指向 `2026-04-01 19:19:39` 生成的 web 快照，持仓数 23；截至 2026-04-02 早晨，未看到新的 selected holdings 主源文件落盘。\n- `ths_local_holdings_selection.json` 当前 `selected_ledger_ids=[]`，说明主链依赖 web/manual source，而不是显式绑定某个本地 ledger；若上午纠正后未写回新的主源文件，系统会继续沿用旧的 23 只快照。\n- 本机同花顺存在多套候选账本，不应凭“数量最多/最新文件”猜主账本；没有新的网页主源/HAR/cURL/显式 ledger 选择时，必须 fail closed，不要假装已经切到新持仓。\n\n## 买入候选链路提醒\n- `quant_p0_p1_guard_rules_v1.json` 中 `P0-004` 仍为 `partial`：盘中/下午重跑必须强制刷新当天 live chain 与 signal tickets，不能只复用上午或昨日产物；后续再出现“今天买入候选跟昨天一样”，优先检查是否真的完成了 force refresh。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775113719142}}
{"type":"message","id":"1356344a","parentId":"72932af4","timestamp":"2026-04-02T07:08:48.382Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to append new memories from this session. Key new durable facts:\n\n1. github-repo-monitor full rollout: 20 repos (main=13, extended=7), tier-based reporting, judgement logic added\n2. Defensive candidate staleness root cause: runtime_risk_state for defensive was generated at 14:20 today (from yesterday's close data), but the morning pipeline at 09:47 ran with yesterday's state → candidates were effectively stale\n3. The morning pipeline at 09:20 ran BEFORE today's runtime_risk_state was generated → it used yesterday's market data\n4. After today's state generated at 14:20, NO second candidate refresh was triggered\n5. Fix direction: add a \"post-close second trigger\" (after 14:00/14:30) to re-run candidate generation with today's actual market state\n\n\n6. Balanced盘的票仓在这两天有替换，但防御盘完全相同，而激进盘今天根本没有候选产生","thinkingSignature":"a18bd7a8da411fdd724c91821d6aecce70e7535e3eccc73787b6a71ecf9a6617"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_y2qs7opgyp1v_1","name":"read","arguments":{"offset":1,"limit":5,"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-04-02.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":15273,"output":264,"cacheRead":15848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31385,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775113719150,"responseId":"061d48f7320579d24502c8f909f7a764"}}
