{"type":"message","id":"2627b7ee","parentId":"10ea6e3d","timestamp":"2026-04-02T07:58:37.541Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gtefh01gm579_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"            lines.append(f\"    {h['qty']:,} 份 | 成本 {h['cost_price']:.3f} 元\")\n\n    lines.append(\"\")\n    lines.append(\"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\")\n    lines.append(f\"【汇总】A股 {len(a_stocks)} 只 | 港股 {len(hk_stocks)} | ETF {len(etf_funds)} 只\")\n    lines.append(f\"持仓总数：{len(holdings)} 只 | 成本总额：{total_cost:,.0f} 元\")\n\n    if strategy:\n        bw = strategy.get(\"market_breadth\")\n        buy = strategy.get(\"buy_count\", 0)\n        sell = strategy.get(\"sell_count\", 0)\n        if bw:\n            icon = \"🟢\" if bw >= 28 else \"🟡\" if bw >= 14 else \"🔴\"\n            lines.append(f\"\\n【市场宽度】{bw:.2f}% {icon}\")\n        if buy or sell:\n            lines.append(f\"【策略信号】BUY {buy} 个 | SELL {sell} 个\")\n        risk_mode = strategy.get(\"risk_mode\", \"\")\n        if risk_mode:\n            lines.append(f\"【风险模式】{risk_mode}\")\n\n    if audit:\n        ar = audit.get(\"annual_return_pct\", 0)\n        mdd = audit.get(\"max_drawdown_pct\", 0)\n        sharpe = audit.get(\"sharpe\", 0)\n        if ar:\n            lines.append(f\"\\n【模拟盘审计】年化 {ar:.1f}% | 回撤 {mdd:.1f}% | 夏普 {sharpe:.2f}\")\n\n    lines.append(\"━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\")\n    lines.append(f\"📊 生成时间：{now.strftime('%H:%M:%S')}\")\n    return \"\\n\".join(lines)\n\n[31 more lines in file. Use offset=170 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775116717532}}
{"type":"message","id":"d73e4ef0","parentId":"2627b7ee","timestamp":"2026-04-02T07:59:05.866Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the full picture. The `get_strategy_summary()` function reads `today_stock_strategy_report_*.md` and extracts the market breadth from it using regex. The strategy report's breadth comes from a pre-generated report, not live data.\n\nThe fix is straightforward:\n1. Add a function `get_live_market_breadth()` that calculates real-time market breadth using akshare\n2. In the main report generation, use this live breadth as a fallback or override\n\nLet me now spawn a Codex session to handle this fix. I have a clear task:\n- File: `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/generate_daily_position_report.py`\n\n\n- I need to add a `get_live_market_breadth()` function using akshare to fetch real-time A-share data and calculate the breadth (up stocks / total stocks), then use this in `get_strategy_summary()` or directly where market breadth is displayed, replacing the stale breadth from the strategy report file.\n\nLet me set up the Codex task now.","thinkingSignature":"561e0a9afdb33d2e9971e9ebc26bd5c26c34ae2cc0a3d047baf9a870a5e12346"},{"type":"text","text":"根因找到了：市场宽度是从 `today_stock_strategy_report_*.md` 文件里用正则表达式解析出来的，那个报告是昨天生成的，所以宽度数据天然是旧的。\n\n修复方案很清晰：**在 `generate_daily_position_report.py` 里加一个 `get_live_market_breadth()` 函数，用 akshare 实时算今天盘中宽度**，然后在生成报告时优先用实时值。\n\n我现在直接交给 Codex 改代码。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_phzh4mesr1h2_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"修复持仓日报市场宽度数据陈旧问题\n\n## 目标文件\n`/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/generate_daily_position_report.py`\n\n## 问题根因\n当前 `get_strategy_summary()` 函数（大约第40-70行）从 `today_stock_strategy_report_*.md` 文件里用正则表达式解析市场宽度：\n```python\nm = re.search(r\"宽度门禁：当前 `([\\d.]+)%`\", content)\n```\n那个策略报告是昨天/前天生成的，宽度数据天然是旧的（昨天 09:17 生成，信号日期是 03-30）。\n\n## 修复方案\n在 `get_strategy_summary()` **之前**插入一个新的 `get_live_market_breadth()` 函数，实时计算今天盘中市场宽度：\n\n```python\ndef get_live_market_breadth():\n    \"\"\"实时计算今日盘中市场宽度：上涨股数/总交易股数\"\"\"\n    import warnings\n    warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\n    try:\n        import akshare as ak\n        df = ak.stock_zh_a_spot_em()\n        total = len(df)\n        up = len(df[df['涨跌幅'] > 0])\n        breadth = up / total * 100 if total > 0 else 0\n        return round(breadth, 2)\n    except Exception:\n        return None\n```\n\n然后在 `get_strategy_summary()` 的 `result` 字典里，尝试调用 `get_live_market_breadth()` 作为 `market_breadth` 的**第一来源**；如果实时接口失败，再 fallback 到正则解析的旧值。\n\n## 约束\n- Python 版本 3.9.6，akshare 可用\n- 函数插入位置要在 `get_strategy_summary()` 定义之前，或直接在其内部调用 `get_live_market_breadth()`\n- 最终 `result[\"market_breadth\"]` 要能正确传递到报告生成处（第148行附近）\n- 不要改其他已有逻辑，只改市场宽度数据来源这一处\n- 改完后运行 `python3 -m py_compile /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/generate_daily_position_report.py` 验证语法\n\n## 验收标准\n1. 语法通过：`python3 -m py_compile` 无报错\n2. 函数 `get_live_market_breadth()` 存在且可单独调用\n3. `get_strategy_summary()` 的 `market_breadth` 字段优先返回实时值（如果有）\n","runtime":"acp","agentId":"codex","mode":"run","cleanup":"keep"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":34616,"output":898,"cacheRead":25866,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61380,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775116717542,"responseId":"061d54ade42d1956d2685f8311fb0d32"}}
