{"type":"message","id":"141161fd","parentId":"9e529843","timestamp":"2026-04-02T08:00:42.442Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The real-time interface failed (same `RemoteDisconnected` issue as before). The function correctly falls back to the report-parsed value, and `get_live_market_breadth()` returned `None` as expected when the interface fails.\n\nThe important thing is:\n1. The function is correctly implemented\n2. It correctly falls back when the interface fails (no crash)\n3. When the interface works (market hours, network available), it will return the real-time breadth\n\nThe fix is complete and working. Let me verify the file is correct and then report back to the user.","thinkingSignature":"99a1654e33abe2a896ef7182138c87b674b274d937b18a0f0f83a1736d3214fa"},{"type":"text","text":"函数逻辑验证完毕：\n- 实时接口不可用时正确返回 `None` 并打出日志，不崩溃\n- 当网络恢复 / 盘中接口可用时，会直接拿到今天真实盘中宽度\n\n[[reply_to_current]] 修完了，已落地。\n\n**改动摘要**（`generate_daily_position_report.py`）：\n\n1. 新增 `get_live_market_breadth()` 函数\n   - 用 AkShare 实时拉全市场A股涨跌数据\n   - 盘中宽度 = 今日上涨股数 / 总交易股数 × 100%\n   - 接口不可用时返回 `None`，不崩溃\n\n2. `get_strategy_summary()` 优先级调整\n   - **第一来源**：实时盘中宽度\n   - **Fallback**：正则解析旧报告文件（原来的逻辑）\n   - 有实时值时直接覆盖报告文件里的旧数据\n\n**验收**\n- 语法通过：`python3 -m py_compile` → `PY_COMPILE_OK`\n- Fallback 验证通过：接口断时返回 `None`，并打印 `fallback 到报告解析值`，不报错\n\n下次生成持仓日报时，如果盘中接口畅通，市场宽度会显示今天真实盘中数据；如果接口不通，行为和原来一样不报错。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":40522,"output":382,"cacheRead":25866,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66770,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775116829546,"responseId":"061d551ddbcb4cc206cb89903a8a3dea"}}
