{"type":"message","id":"2f067043","parentId":"3e0b398e","timestamp":"2026-04-02T10:54:39.049Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"张玲希望市场宽度旁边备注一下生成时间。我需要修改 `build_report()` 函数，在显示市场宽度时加上时间戳。\n\n对于实时盘中宽度：应该显示当前时间（因为是实时拉的）\n对于从报告文件解析的：应该显示报告文件的时间\n\n我需要：\n1. 在 `get_live_market_breadth()` 返回值里加上时间\n2. 在 `get_strategy_summary()` 里追踪宽度的来源和时间\n3. 在 `build_report()` 里把时间显示出来\n\n更简洁的做法：\n- `get_live_market_breadth()` 返回 `(breadth, timestamp)` 元组，或在返回 `breadth` 的同时，在 `get_strategy_summary()` 里记录一个 `market_breadth_source` 和 `market_breadth_fetched_at` 字段\n\n\n- 或者在 `strategy` dict 里加一个 `market_breadth_fetch_time` 字段\n\n我可以利用 `datetime.now()` 格式化到分钟，然后直接在报告里显示。","thinkingSignature":"781ef05d51b5664bc013c64e6914c1e48c5e28f4435def0f397b0f1783cc0f15"},{"type":"text","text":"\n收到，加时间戳。我直接在策略 dict 里塞一个 `market_breadth_fetch_time`，然后在 `build_report()` 里拼进去。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8mqwf4eq6l6b_1","name":"read","arguments":{"offset":50,"limit":30,"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/generate_daily_position_report.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4,"output":295,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":31144,"totalTokens":31443,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775127270335,"responseId":"061d7de644b6073b04adb7beab9c49f5"}}
