{"type":"message","id":"88ced6dc","parentId":"05a80d89","timestamp":"2026-04-02T10:58:15.809Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found the key line at 173:\n```python\n# 不再按\"财经内容\"过滤；所有抓到的微博均进入汇总分析\nstock_posts.append((text, created_at, post_url))\n```\n\nSo the issue is at line 173 - it's no longer filtering anything, all posts are being appended. The fix needs to add a content quality filter there.\n\nAlso looking at the post that was pushed - it had `评论分析（0条）` and just hashtags with no real content. I need to add a filter that skips posts where:\n1. The text is just hashtags (no meaningful content after stripping hashtags)\n2. Or the text is too short (below a character threshold)\n\n\n3. Or maybe skip if `评论数 == 0` and it's not from a key opinion leader\n\nLet me check what data fields are available for each post to implement these filters properly.","thinkingSignature":"b797e7783f4b5209246c2dbf15989c75e00ecc991530489480071cc04eecc3bc"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_izooqzl3muuc_1","name":"read","arguments":{"offset":60,"limit":60,"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/weibo-monitor/scripts/fetch_weibo.py"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_izooqzl3muuc_2","name":"read","arguments":{"offset":120,"limit":80,"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/weibo-monitor/scripts/fetch_weibo.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":38510,"output":302,"cacheRead":25866,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64678,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775127486687,"responseId":"061d7ebeb29d1d78a671a19484789e91"}}
{"type":"message","id":"65454cb4","parentId":"88ced6dc","timestamp":"2026-04-02T10:58:15.936Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_izooqzl3muuc_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    return posts[:limit], user_info\n\ndef parse_text(post):\n    \"\"\"解析微博文本内容\"\"\"\n    # 微博返回的文本可能在 text 或 text_raw 字段\n    text = post.get(\"text_raw\", post.get(\"text\", \"\"))\n    # 清理 HTML 标签\n    import re\n    text = re.sub(r'<[^>]+>', '', text)\n    text = text.replace('&nbsp;', ' ').replace('&amp;', '&').replace('&lt;', '<').replace('&gt;', '>')\n    return text.strip()\n\ndef is_stock_related(text):\n    \"\"\"简单判断内容是否与股票/金融市场相关\"\"\"\n    keywords = [\n        \"股票\", \"A股\", \"大盘\", \"上证\", \"深证\", \"创业板\", \"科创板\", \"北证\",\n        \"指数\", \"涨跌\", \"涨停\", \"跌停\", \"持仓\", \"建仓\", \"清仓\", \"加仓\", \"减仓\",\n        \"牛市\", \"熊市\", \"回调\", \"反弹\", \"突破\", \"支撑\", \"压力\",\n        \"板块\", \"概念\", \"龙头\", \"庄家\", \"主力\", \"资金\", \"量能\", \"缩量\", \"放量\",\n        \"研报\", \"业绩\", \"财报\", \"PE\", \"PB\", \"估值\", \"股息\", \"分红\",\n        \"期权\", \"期货\", \"融资\", \"融券\", \"杠杆\", \"做空\", \"做多\",\n        \"美联储\", \"加息\", \"降息\", \"美股\", \"港股\", \"汇率\", \"人民币\", \"美元\",\n        \"央行\", \"货币政策\", \"经济数据\", \"CPI\", \"PPI\", \"GDP\",\n        \"宁德\", \"茅台\", \"比亚迪\", \"腾讯\", \"阿里\", \"美团\", \"京东\",\n        \"新能源\", \"半导体\", \"芯片\", \"AI\", \"人工智能\", \"医药\", \"白酒\",\n        \"证券\", \"基金\", \"私募\", \"公募\", \"量化\", \"对冲\",\n    ]\n    text_lower = text.lower()\n    return sum(1 for kw in keywords if kw in text) >= 2\n\ndef send_feishu(webhook, message):\n    \"\"\"发送飞书消息\"\"\"\n    payload = {\n        \"msg_type\": \"text\",\n        \"content\": {\"text\": message}\n    }\n    resp = requests.post(webhook, json=payload, timeout=10)\n    return resp.json()\n\ndef get_state_file():\n    \"\"\"获取状态文件路径（记录上次抓取的最新微博ID）\"\"\"\n    return Path(__file__).parent.parent / \"config\" / \"last_post_id.txt\"\n\ndef load_last_post_id():\n    \"\"\"加载上次已处理的最新微博ID\"\"\"\n    sf = get_state_file()\n    if sf.exists():\n        return sf.read_text().strip()\n    return None\n\ndef save_last_post_id(post_id):\n    \"\"\"保存最新微博ID\"\"\"\n    get_state_file().write_text(str(post_id))\n\ndef main():\n    # 默认监控的微博 UID\n    DEFAULT_UID = \"2014433131\"\n    \n    uid = sys.argv[1] if len(sys.argv) > 1 else DEFAULT_UID\n    limit = int(sys.argv[2]) if len(sys.argv) > 2 else 10\n\n[90 more lines in file. Use offset=120 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775127495918}}
{"type":"message","id":"6f0d81a7","parentId":"65454cb4","timestamp":"2026-04-02T10:58:15.959Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_izooqzl3muuc_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    \n    cookie = load_cookie()\n    if not cookie:\n        print(\"错误: 未找到微博 Cookie，请检查 config/cookie.env\")\n        sys.exit(1)\n    \n    print(f\"[{datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')}] 开始抓取微博 UID={uid}\")\n    \n    posts, user_info = fetch_weibo(uid, cookie, limit)\n    \n    if not posts:\n        print(\"未获取到微博，可能 Cookie 已过期\")\n        sys.exit(1)\n    \n    username = user_info.get(\"name\", user_info.get(\"screen_name\", \"未知用户\"))\n    print(f\"博主: {username}, 获取到 {len(posts)} 条微博\")\n    \n    # 检查是否有新微博（跳过置顶帖，避免置顶命中状态导致漏检）\n    last_id = load_last_post_id()\n    effective_posts = [post for post in posts if not post.get(\"isTop\")]\n    last_id_is_top = any(str(post.get(\"idstr\", \"\")) == last_id and post.get(\"isTop\") for post in posts)\n    new_posts = []\n\n    if last_id_is_top:\n        print(\"检测到旧状态命中了置顶帖，切换为非置顶微博基线\")\n        today_token = datetime.now().strftime(\"%a %b %d\")\n        for post in effective_posts:\n            created_at = str(post.get(\"created_at\", \"\"))\n            if created_at.startswith(today_token):\n                new_posts.append(post)\n            else:\n                break\n    else:\n        for post in effective_posts:\n            post_id = str(post.get(\"idstr\", \"\"))\n            if post_id == last_id:\n                break\n            new_posts.append(post)\n    \n    # 反转顺序（按时间正序）\n    new_posts = new_posts[::-1]\n    \n    webhook = load_feishu_webhook()\n    \n    if new_posts:\n        print(f\"发现 {len(new_posts)} 条新微博\")\n        \n        stock_posts = []\n        for post in new_posts:\n            text = parse_text(post)\n            created_at = post.get(\"created_at\", \"\")\n            post_url = f\"https://weibo.com/{uid}/{post.get('idstr', '')}\"\n            \n            # 不再按\"财经内容\"过滤；所有抓到的微博均进入汇总分析\n            stock_posts.append((text, created_at, post_url))\n        \n        # 发送通知\n        if stock_posts:\n            msg = f\"📢 【{username}】新发微博（{len(stock_posts)} 条）\\n\\n\"\n            for i, (text, created_at, url) in enumerate(stock_posts[:5], 1):\n                msg += f\"{i}. {text[:100]}\"\n                if len(text) > 100:\n                    msg += \"...\"\n                msg += f\"\\n   {url}\\n\\n\"\n            \n            if len(stock_posts) > 5:\n                msg += f\"...还有 {len(stock_posts) - 5} 条\\n\"\n        else:\n            msg = f\"📢 【{username}】新发微博 {len(new_posts)} 条\"\n        \n        send_feishu(webhook, msg)\n        \n        # 保存最新微博ID\n        save_last_post_id(str(new_posts[-1].get(\"idstr\", \"\")))\n        \n    else:\n        print(\"没有新微博\")\n    \n    # 输出所有抓取的微博（调试用）\n    print(\"\\n--- 最近微博 ---\")\n\n[10 more lines in file. Use offset=200 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775127495937}}
{"type":"message","id":"8c134e44","parentId":"6f0d81a7","timestamp":"2026-04-02T10:58:25.265Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the issue. At line 173, there's a comment that says \"不再按'财经内容'过滤；所有抓到的微博均进入汇总分析\" - meaning all posts go through without filtering. But there's also the `is_stock_related()` function that's defined but not actually used for filtering new posts.\n\nLooking at the push that was sent:\n- It had just hashtags `#杨德龙 # #A股#` with no real text content\n- Comments analysis showed 0 comments\n\nI need to add a filter that:\n1. Skips posts that are basically just hashtags with no meaningful text content\n2. Strips hashtags and checks if the remaining text has at least some meaningful content (e.g., > 10 chars of non-hashtag content)\n\n\n3. The current code doesn't evaluate comments in the filtering step at all\n\nI think the simplest approach is to add a helper function that strips hashtags and evaluates whether there's substantive text left, then skip posts that fail this check before they get pushed to the notification.","thinkingSignature":"d74ad7ded1a9696206f3539cb3e80c28f112678d3310fbeb2ea477d7a249d98e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_i24muoqcpvxs_1","name":"read","arguments":{"offset":1,"limit":5,"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/weibo-monitor/scripts/fetch_weibo.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":40269,"output":273,"cacheRead":25866,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66408,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775127495960,"responseId":"061d7ec84fdfe22c8d461a7e195deafd"}}
