{"type":"message","id":"28888f91","parentId":"ba518d1d","timestamp":"2026-04-02T10:59:13.880Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The filter works correctly:\n- Pure hashtag posts (like `#杨德龙 # #A股#`) → False (filtered out)\n- Normal posts with content → True (kept)\n- Posts that are only hashtags without meaningful content → False (filtered)\n- Posts with just links → False (filtered)\n\nNow let me also quickly check the `fetch_weibo_v2.py` to see if it has the same issue.","thinkingSignature":"ab8bcbc463fe20eb8ca0821091e3fa0352cbcd62ebc42d1578ce5a9c6fde967a"},{"type":"text","text":"过滤逻辑验证通过。再顺手检查 v2 是否有同样的问题：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8haa0tsx0gv3_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n 'stock_posts.append\\|不再按.*过滤\\|has_meaningful' /Users/ling/.openclaw/skills/weibo-monitor/scripts/fetch_weibo_v2.py 2>/dev/null | head -10","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":42468,"output":200,"cacheRead":25866,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68534,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775127546533,"responseId":"061d7efbfcc63d9b350d5ca6a453c101"}}
