{"type":"message","id":"bcf43fcc","parentId":"957a63a3","timestamp":"2026-04-02T10:59:27.169Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The fix is confirmed. Let me update memory to record this fix.","thinkingSignature":"47b1971f5f79baaa544c83ee82d1d3357a7437dacdb151eb321aa27bb2ec2cc4"},{"type":"text","text":"已修复并验证。\n\n[[reply_to_current]] 修完了，已落地。\n\n**问题根因**：第 173 行写着\"不再按财经内容过滤\"，所以纯标签微博（如 `#杨德龙 # #A股#`）直接进了推送，没有任何内容质量判断。\n\n**改动**：\n1. 新增 `has_meaningful_content()` 过滤函数——去除 `#标签#` 和 URL 后，有效字符少于 10 个的微博直接跳过\n2. append 到 `stock_posts` 前加拦截逻辑，不符合条件的打印 `[过滤] 无实质内容: ...` 并 continue\n\n**验证**：\n- `#杨德龙 # #A股#` → 0 有意义字符 → **过滤掉，不推送**\n- 正常微博 → **保留推送**\n\n下次同花顺/大V发纯标签微博就不会再骚扰你了。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":42970,"output":191,"cacheRead":25866,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69027,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775127560787,"responseId":"061d7f085d48a2d3998aadb2d7769485"}}
