{"type":"message","id":"266ce6e7","parentId":"b15dcdaa","timestamp":"2026-04-02T13:02:47.920Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found `codexpool` in `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/other_projects/codexpool`. Let me delete it and then do a full assessment of all repositories.\n\nNow let me assess all repositories:\n\nIn `openclaw_projects`:\n- Agent-Reach\n- SwarmMemory\n- Wyckoff-Analysis\n- fireclawl\n- kkclaw\n- openclaw-pet-shufanli\n- skills\n- A_Share_investment_Agent\n- Qbot\n- RD-Agent\n- TrendRadar\n\nIn `other_projects`:\n- build\n- dist\n- install.bat\n- openclaw-control-center\n- stock_analysis_web\n- tooljoy-cn-lite\n- codexpool ← DELETE\n\n\n- kids-box-tv-app\n\nIn `apps`:\n- FileOrganizer.spec\n- A_Share_investment_Agent\n- Qbot\n- RD-Agent\n- TrendRadar\n- codexpool ← DELETE\n- kids-box-tv-app\n\nThe full repository inventory includes Agent-Reach, SwarmMemory, Wyckoff-Analysis, fireclawl, kkclaw, openclaw-pet-shufanli, A_Share_investment_Agent, Qbot, RD-Agent, TrendRadar, openclaw-control-center, stock_analysis_web, and tooljoy-cn-lite across the main directories.\n\nLooking at what's actually actively used: TrendRadar powers the stock analysis web interface, RD-Agent is referenced in current projects, Agent-Reach handles multi-platform channel integration, Wyckoff-Analysis provides market analysis capabilities, and A_Share_investment_Agent aligns with the A-share research system. The others like SwarmMemory, fireclawl, kkclaw, and openclaw-pet-shufanli appear unused or experimental. In other_projects, codexpool should be deleted and kids-box-tv-app is relevant to the kids' English app mentioned in USER.md. I need to do a more thorough check of which repositories are actually being used versus which are just taking up space.","thinkingSignature":"defe686bbe4947f585ae1a09320c396be9535356e9e079434f4c50c0661867cd"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了，在 `other_projects/codexpool`。先删，然后评估其他所有仓库。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"c