{"type":"message","id":"2a3b55ee","parentId":"144f897c","timestamp":"2026-04-02T13:04:17.699Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clearer picture. Let me assess each repo:\n\n**Active/In-use:**\n1. **Agent-Reach** (`openclaw_projects/`) - 102 commits ahead of remote, last used 2026-03-05, active development\n2. **TrendRadar** (`other_projects/`) - used in `aggregate_intelligence_brief.py`, actively generating reports\n3. **openclaw-control-center** (`other_projects/`) - 44 commits ahead, active development\n4. **kids-box-tv-app** (`other_projects/`) - main focus per USER.md (kids English app)\n\n\n5. **A_Share_investment_Agent**, **Qbot**, and **RD-Agent** across both directories have no git history and appear to be dormant projects, with Qbot likely superseded by the kids English app effort\n\n**Experimental/Uncertain:**\n6. **Wyckoff-Analysis** (`openclaw_projects/`) - 120 commits ahead with recent activity, used in intelligence reports\n7. **SwarmMemory** (`openclaw_projects/`) - synced with remote\n8. **openclaw-pet-shufanli** (`openclaw_projects/`) - synced with remote\n9. **fireclawl** and **kkclaw** (`openclaw_projects/`) - both lack git tracking and look abandoned or experimental\n10. **stock_analysis_web** (`other_projects/`) - no git, appears to be a discontinued web interface\n11. **tooljoy-cn-lite** (`other_projects/`) - minor project with 2 commits ahead\n12. **skills** (`openclaw_projects/`) - contains skill directories\n\nI notice that `A_Share_investment_Agent`, `Qbot`, `RD-Agent`, and `TrendRadar` appear in both `openclaw_projects/` and `apps/` without git tracking. Now I'm checking what these duplicates actually are in the apps directory.","thinkingSignature":"523c6802ddb573b56b2d2ee106c24c292500ad25fb06b72b77eec4133b20f451"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_fitifp2d9l8p_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查 apps 里那几个无 git 的项目是什么\nfor d in /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/A_Share_i