{"type":"message","id":"02c20715","parentId":"6a9033d6","timestamp":"2026-04-02T13:04:53.849Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting findings:\n\n1. **fireclawl** - only 1 file, 1 directory. Essentially empty/minimal. Probably an abandoned scaffold.\n2. **kkclaw** - 11,023 files, 1,932 directories. This is a **massive** project with SKILL.md, CONTRIBUTING.md, etc. This is not a toy - it has substantial content. Let me check what it is.\n3. **stock_analysis_web** - only 2 files (app.py and templates dir). Old web project, small. Probably not used.\n4. **kids-box-tv-app** - NO_GIT, can't even run git log. \n\nIt's not tracked in version control. Now I need to dig into kkclaw since it's a substantial project - and I notice USER.md flags \"少儿英语 App / kids English App\" as a current priority, so let me see if kkclaw is related to that or something else entirely.","thinkingSignature":"3f82dc8cc8aa5de79acea0eed433c0f494f098a33a35aadc7fae76b18aa9e7e0"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_d9nf2t7rxn4h_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"head -20 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/openclaw_projects/kkclaw/README.md 2>/dev/null\n# 看 fireclawl 那个唯一文件是什么\nls /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/openclaw_projects/fireclawl/","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":15}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_d9nf2t7rxn4h_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# kids-box-tv-app 内容\nls /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/other_projects/kids-box-tv-app/ | head -15\nfind /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/other_projects/kids-box-tv-app -type f | wc -l | xargs echo \"files:\"","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":49553,"output":420,"cacheRead":25640,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75613,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775135081652,"responseId":"0