{"type":"message","id":"c935f61f","parentId":"02c20715","timestamp":"2026-04-02T13:04:53.919Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_d9nf2t7rxn4h_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 🦞 KKClaw Desktop Pet\n\n**[English](#-english) | [中文](#-中文)**\n\n---\n\n<a id=\"-中文\"></a>\n\n## 🇨🇳 中文\n\n**OpenClaw 桌面可视化伴侣 — 流体玻璃球宠物、14情绪系统、声音克隆（MiniMax TTS）、一键配置向导、Gateway 智能守护**\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n\n![Hero Banner](docs/images/hero-banner.png)\n\n*OpenClaw Core + Desktop Embodiment = A living interface with emotion, voice, and presence*\n\n[![Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/version-3.5.2-FF6B4A?style=for-the-badge&logo=github)](https://github.com/kk43994/kkclaw/releases)\n[![CI](https://img.shields.io/github/actions/workflow/status/kk43994/kkclaw/ci.yml?style=for-the-badge&logo=github-actions&logoColor=white&label=CI)](https://github.com/kk43994/kkclaw/actions/workflows/ci.yml)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":16,"aggregated":"# 🦞 KKClaw Desktop Pet\n\n**[English](#-english) | [中文](#-中文)**\n\n---\n\n<a id=\"-中文\"></a>\n\n## 🇨🇳 中文\n\n**OpenClaw 桌面可视化伴侣 — 流体玻璃球宠物、14情绪系统、声音克隆（MiniMax TTS）、一键配置向导、Gateway 智能守护**\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n\n![Hero Banner](docs/images/hero-banner.png)\n\n*OpenClaw Core + Desktop Embodiment = A living interface with emotion, voice, and presence*\n\n[![Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/version-3.5.2-FF6B4A?style=for-the-badge&logo=github)](https://github.com/kk43994/kkclaw/releases)\n[![CI](https://img.shields.io/github/actions/workflow/status/kk43994/kkclaw/ci.yml?style=for-the-badge&logo=github-actions&logoColor=white&label=CI)](https://github.com/kk43994/kkclaw/actions/workflows/ci.yml)","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775135093891}}
