nalysis_web` are definitely dead weight. For `openclaw_projects/skills`, I should estimate the space savings before making a final recommendation. I'm also realizing `codexpool` is already deleted, so that's one less thing to worry about.","thinkingSignature":"43d0fee838bbe3f46524d28de7a2534b0f266675a343243a10284e9ab7fd6252"},{"type":"text","text":"评估完毕，结论清晰了。\n\n[[reply_to_current]] 汇报：\n\n**已删除**\n- `apps/codexpool` ✅ 已删\n\n**强烈建议删除（无用）**\n\n| 仓库 | 大小 | 原因 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `openclaw_projects/fireclawl` | ~1文件 | 只含一个 `.gitignore`，完全空项目，无任何引用 |\n| `other_projects/stock_analysis_web` | ~2文件 | 古老 Flask 监控页，代码里硬编码 Tushare token（泄漏风险），无 git，已多年未动 |\n\n**可删也可留（影响小）**\n\n| 仓库 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| `openclaw_projects/skills/` | 32个 skill，其中 ~20个与 `~/.openclaw/skills/` 完全重复；占空间但不碍事 |\n| `apps/A_Share_investment_Agent` 等 | 空目录（0文件），不影响运行，删了界面干净 |\n\n**需保留的**\n- `kids-box-tv-app`（`apps/`）：少儿英语 App 主项目，Gradle Android，2392 文件，**USER.md 当前主任务**\n- `kkclaw`：桌面宠物伴侣，功能完整，102 commits ahead\n- `Agent-Reach`：多平台 channel 集成，120 commits ahead\n- `Wyckoff-Analysis`：威科夫分析，被 intelligence brief 引用\n- `openclaw-control-center`：OpenClaw 控制面板，44 commits ahead\n\n---\n\n**要我现在把 fireclawl 和 stock_analysis_web 这两个删掉吗？** 确认后即执行。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":52651,"output":837,"cacheRead":25640,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79128,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775135144874,"responseId":"061d9ca9dc58b1b2bd3e7089d45d8983"}}
