worktrees like A_Share, Qbot, and RD-Agent. I need to emphasize that these are actual repositories mapped through worktrees, not just duplicates, so I should exercise caution before deleting. I ought to check their current usage in workspace scripts and evaluate factors like how active they are, their age, size, and whether they're external. It might be useful to suggest tiers for deletion, and I've removed some candidates already.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Identifying candidates for deletion**\\n\\nI’m considering repositories for deletion if the user no longer wants the alt investment agent. There are those like Qbot, which has no workspace references and is a huge external worktree, possibly obsolete. RD-Agent is also external and unrelated to current priorities. Then there's SwarmMemory, an old experiment with no relevance. Some others, like openclaw-pet-shufanli and kkclaw, are nonessential but might be useful depending on the user’s needs. I should clarify which worktrees are really inactive and caution the user about potential impacts on existing projects.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Confirming tasks and memory checks**\\n\\nIt seems I don't need to check if openclaw-pet-shufanli and kkclaw overlap. I should probably mention that \\\"我已切到 gpt-5.4\\\" since the user asked about the switch. We've already switched, which is good to clarify. I think I might also say, \\\"我查了记忆和当前目录,\\\" but I’m unsure if I need to cite memory searches again. Maybe it’s better not to ask about that again at this point. I just want to make sure I’m providing clear updates!\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 已按 **gpt-5.4** 重新审核，这次只基于**当前真实目录 + 当前实际引用**来给建议，不沿用前面那版口头判断。\n\n### 先说结论\n**我建议下一批优先考虑删除的，是这 6 个：**\n\n#### 第一档：高概率没用，优先删\n1. `other_projects/Qbot`\n   - 当前 workspace **无任何引用**\n   - 不在你当前主线（量化主线 / 少儿英语 App）\n   - 体量大、历史包袱重\n   - **结论：高优先级可删**\n\n2. `other_projects/RD-Agent`\n   - 当前 workspace **无任何引用**\n   - 和你当前主任务无关\n   - 是外部 worktree 映射，不是本地新项目\n   - **结论：高优先级可删**\n\n3. `openclaw_projects/SwarmMemory`\n   - 只有历史部署记录，当前 **无实际引用**\n   - 不属于你当前主线\n   - 体积小，但纯占位\n   - **结论：可删**\n\n4. `openclaw_projects/openclaw-pet-shufanli`\n   - 当前 **无任何引用**\n   - 偏陪伴/宠物类，不属于当前业务重点\n   - **结论：可删**\n\n#### 第二档：大概率没用，但建议你拍板一次\n5. `other_projects/A_Share_investment_Agent`\n   - 当前 workspace **无引用**\n   - 名字像量化相关，但你主线已经是 `personal-a-share-research-system`\n   - 它还是个 **外部真实仓库映射**，删的是 worktree，不只是空目录\n   - **结论：大概率可删，但建议你明确确认**\n\n6. `other_projects/tooljoy-cn-lite`\n   - 当前 workspace **无引用**\n   - 小项目，非主线\n   - **结论：可删**\n\n---\n\n### 暂时建议保留\n1. `apps/kids-box-tv-app`\n   - 这是你当前主任务，**必须保留**\n\n2. `other_projects/TrendRadar`\n   - 被 `scripts/aggregate_intelligence_brief.py` 直接引用\n   - **当前在用**\n\n3. `openclaw_projects/Wyckoff-Analysis`\n   - 虽然当前主线里引用不多，但它是完整量化/分析项目，且体量大\n   - **先不建议贸然删**\n\n4. `openclaw_projects/Agent-Reach`\n   - 多平台接入能力仓\n   - 虽然当前脚本没直接引用，但有明确能力价值\n   - **先留**\n\n5. `other_projects/openclaw-control-center`\n   - 控制中心项目，虽然当前脚本没直接引用，但功能上是可复用基础设施\n   - **先留**\n\n6. `openclaw_projects/kkclaw`\n   - 体积大（约 494M），但它是完整桌宠/伴侣项目，不是残废仓\n   - 如果你明确不用桌宠体系，再删更稳\n   - **暂列观察，不作为本轮首删**\n\n---\n\n### 一个重要提醒\n`Qbot`、`RD-Agent`、`A_Share_investment_Agent` 这三个，**不是普通小目录**，它们的 Git 顶层指向外部卷：\n- `A_Share_investment_Agent` → `/Volumes/A/openclaw-cold/...`\n- `Qbot` → `/Volumes/A/openclaw-cold/...`\n- `RD-Agent` → `/Volumes/A/openclaw-cold/...`\n\n也就是说它们是 **worktree/映射仓**。  \n删掉当前目录本身没问题，但我会把它们当作**较高风险删除**来处理，不会混同于删普通缓存目录。\n\n---\n\n### 我的建议删单\n如果你要我下一步直接执行，我建议按这个顺序：\n\n**建议先删：**\n- `other_projects/Qbot`\n- `other_projects/RD-Agent`\n- `openclaw_projects/SwarmMemory`\n- `openclaw_projects/openclaw-pet-shufanli`\n- `other_projects/tooljoy-cn-lite`\n\n**单独确认后再删：**\n- `other_projects/A_Share_investment_Agent`\n\n你如果愿意，我下一条就直接给你出一版**“建议删除名单 v2（含风险等级）”**，你只要回复“按 v2 删除”，我就直接执行。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_09a911b5fc3aeb120169ce6c0fefe8819b9e79f2b916702471\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":472,"output":1533,"cacheRead":97280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99285,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775135742590,"responseId":"resp_09a911b5fc3aeb120169ce6bffcd28819baf6b8840edc3a27f"}}
