=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering file deletions and audits**\\n\\nI think I should check if the openclaw-control-center is properly referenced, and maybe consider suggesting its deletion. The build and dist seem safe to delete too. I need to commit the deletion of A_share once it's done, updating the active task. After that, maybe I should produce an audit before committing again. The user asked for a deletion and audit, so I can directly share the audit results and commit hash or create a file with a summary if needed.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Creating a report for workspace maintenance**\\n\\nIt looks like the AGENTS suggest keeping deliverables to a minimum, but since this involves multiple steps, I think it’s best to create a report file. I’ll put it in the research or deliverables section, maybe naming it `repo_trim_audit_20260402.md`. I might not need any special skills for this. I’ll summarize the remaining repositories in the report, then commit the deletions and update the ACTIVE_TASK after each step. Time to get started on that report!\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"我顺手落一个审计文件，后面你要复盘就不用翻聊天记录。\n","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_09a911b5fc3aeb120169ce70102100819bbd0a4685dd2827f3\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_NFN5XjnhHkT7tmhmxP2SRRzO|fc_09a911b5fc3aeb120169ce70102d00819b8822caccb5c355d3","name":"write","arguments":{"file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/repo_trim_audit_20260402.md","content":"# 仓库瘦身审计（2026-04-02 21:34）\n\n## 已执行删除\n- apps/codexpool\n- openclaw_projects/fireclawl\n- other_projects/stock_analysis_web\n- openclaw_projects/skills\n- other_projects/Qbot\n- other_projects/RD-Agent\n- openclaw_projects/SwarmMemory\n- openclaw_projects/openclaw-pet-shufanli\n- other_projects/tooljoy-cn-lite\n- other_projects/A_Share_investment_Agent（删除的是 workspace 内符号链接入口，不碰外部卷真实仓）\n\n## 当前剩余目录\n- apps/kids-box-tv-app\n- openclaw_projects/Agent-Reach\n- openclaw_projects/Wyckoff-Analysis\n- openclaw_projects/kkclaw\n- other_projects/TrendRadar\n- other_projects/openclaw-control-center\n- other_projects/build\n- other_projects/dist\n\n## 分组建议\n\n### 保留\n1. `apps/kids-box-tv-app`\n   - 当前主任务项目（少儿英语 App）\n   - 约 185M\n2. `other_projects/TrendRadar`\n   - 被 `scripts/aggregate_intelligence_brief.py` 直接引用\n   - 约 102M\n3. `openclaw_projects/Agent-Reach`\n   - 多平台接入能力仓，体积小（约 2.5M）\n   - 先保留\n\n### 观察\n1. `other_projects/openclaw-control-center`\n   - 当前脚本未直接引用\n   - 但属于 OpenClaw 控制面板类基础设施\n   - 约 91M，建议暂观察\n2. `openclaw_projects/Wyckoff-Analysis`\n   - 历史上明确部署过\n   - 当前直接引用较少，但属完整分析项目\n   - 约 653M，建议观察后决定\n3. `openclaw_projects/kkclaw`\n   - 桌宠/伴侣项目\n   - 当前无直接引用\n   - 约 494M，若明确不用桌宠体系，可进入下一批删除\n\n### 建议删除（下一批优先）\n1. `other_projects/build`\n   - PyInstaller 构建中间产物\n   - 约 11M\n2. `other_projects/dist`\n   - `FileOrganizer.app` 打包产物\n   - 约 16M\n\n## 当前最值得继续删的目标\n- `other_projects/build`\n- `other_projects/dist`\n- 若你明确不用桌宠：`openclaw_projects/kkclaw`\n- 若你确认控制台不再需要：`other_projects/openclaw-control-center`\n- 若你确认威科夫分析不再需要：`openclaw_projects/Wyckoff-Analysis`\n"},"partialJson":"{\"file\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/repo_trim_audit_20260402.md\",\"content\":\"# 仓库瘦身审计（2026-04-02 21:34）\\n\\n## 已执行删除\\n- apps/codexpool\\n- openclaw_projects/fireclawl\\n- other_projects/stock_analysis_web\\n- openclaw_projects/skills\\n- other_projects/Qbot\\n- other_projects/RD-Agent\\n- openclaw_projects/SwarmMemory\\n- openclaw_projects/openclaw-pet-shufanli\\n- other_projects/tooljoy-cn-lite\\n- other_projects/A_Share_investment_Agent（删除的是 workspace 内符号链接入口，不碰外部卷真实仓）\\n\\n## 当前剩余目录\\n- apps/kids-box-tv-app\\n- openclaw_projects/Agent-Reach\\n- openclaw_projects/Wyckoff-Analysis\\n- openclaw_projects/kkclaw\\n- other_projects/TrendRadar\\n- other_projects/openclaw-control-center\\n- other_projects/build\\n- other_projects/dist\\n\\n## 分组建议\\n\\n### 保留\\n1. `apps/kids-box-tv-app`\\n   - 当前主任务项目（少儿英语 App）\\n   - 约 185M\\n2. `o